NK032(khi)005:1: // bsnyan brgyud rdo rje zam pa'i lo rgyus 'bring po gdams ngag dang bcas pa bzhugs so //
NK032(khi)005:2: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)005:3: gdod nas dag pa'i byang chub sems nyid kyi //
NK032(khi)005:4: nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa /
NK032(khi)005:5: bya ba la sogs pa'i don ston pa lags so //
NK032(khi)005:6: de la spyir gdams ngag gi lugs kyi mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)005:7: mchod par brjod pa rgyud lung ngam sgrub thab sam bstan bcos las 'byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:8: gdams ngag la mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK032(khi)005:10: rang gi rgyud la nyams su myong tshod dam /
NK032(khi)005:12: rtogs tshod kyi don nyung la 'dus par ston pas na /
NK032(khi)005:13: klad kyi don mchod par brjod pa mi 'byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:14: 'byung na'ang brgyud pa'i bla ma la mchod par brjod pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:17: bstan bcos la mchod par brjod pa 'byung ba'i rgyu mtshan ni /
NK032(khi)005:19: sgrub thabs kyi gtso bo'i lha'am /
NK032(khi)005:20: bstan bcos rtsom pa po rten gyi gang zag gis yi dam gyi lha'am /
NK032(khi)005:21: yang na bstan pa'i bdag po la mchod par brjod pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:24: mjug bsdu ba la sogs pa mang la 'brel bar ston pa yin pas na /
NK032(khi)005:25: klad kyi don mchod par brjod par 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)005:26: de yang ma rtogs pa rtogs par bya ba'i thabs
NK032(khi)005:27: kun rdzob lus ngag yid gsum gyi phyag yul gzhan
NK032(khi)005:29: gdams ngag rdo rje zam pa 'di ni rgyud dang gdams ngag yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:31: de yang yul gzhan la mchod par mi brjod de /
NK032(khi)005:32: rtogs pa'i don de gsal 'debs pa shes rab don
NK032(khi)005:33: dam pa'i phyag nyid la nyid kyis mchod par brjod
NK032(khi)005:34: pa'o // de yang rdzogs pa chen po gu ru bzhi pa las /
NK032(khi)005:35: sems las sangs rgyas med pas mchod pa gzhan mi bya /
NK032(khi)005:37: kun tu bzang po che ba rang la gnas pa'i rgyud las /
NK032(khi)005:38: chos kyi dbyings na gcig pur bzhugs pa'i lha //
NK032(khi)005:39: don dam byang chub sems kyi lha yin te //
NK032(khi)005:40: don dam sems kyi lha la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)005:42: rdo rje zam pa'i rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)005:43: rtogs pa'i rig pa gnyis med ngang du 'dud //
NK032(khi)005:45: gnyis su med pa'i don brjod du med pa'i ngang gcig tu 'dud pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:46: de yang tshul la thabs ji ltar du mchod par brjod pa na /
NK032(khi)005:47: ma nor ma bcos bsam 'das brjod med ngang la phyag 'tshal lo //
NK032(khi)005:49: de la dang po ma nor zhes pa'i don ni /
NK032(khi)005:50: chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don /
NK032(khi)005:51: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs /
NK032(khi)005:52: rang byung gi ye shes chen po /
NK032(khi)005:57: chos bzhi dang ldan pa de bla mas brda dang
NK032(khi)005:58: ngag gis ngo sprad nas phyin ci ma log par
NK032(khi)005:59: rtog pas na ma nor zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:60: ma nor pa'i don de la yar sangs rgyas sgam ste mdzad du mi btub /
NK032(khi)005:61: mar sems can sgrin te bsgyur du mi btub /
NK032(khi)005:62: bar gang zag gi blos bcos su med pas na ma bcos zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:63: ma bcos pa'i don de yid yul lam /
NK032(khi)005:65: dran yul la mi gnas te bsam du ma btub pas na bsam 'das zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:66: bsam las 'das pa'i don de blo'i yul lam /
NK032(khi)005:68: tshig gi yul la mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)005:69: smra ru ma btub pas na brjod med ces bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:70: brjod du med pa'i don de las mi 'da' zhing mi 'gyur bar gnas pas na ngang zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:71: don dam bsam 'das brjod du med pa'i ngang de rang yin par ngos 'dzin pa las /
NK032(khi)005:72: de las lhag pa'i don zhig gzhan nas btsal du med pas na la zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:73: bsam 'das brjod du med pa'i ngang de la /
NK032(khi)005:74: gzung 'dzin bag chags kyi rtog pa rdul tsam pa
NK032(khi)005:75: zhig kyang mi gnas par phyags pas na phyag ces
NK032(khi)005:76: bya'o // gzung 'dzin gyi bag chags mi gnas pa'i
NK032(khi)005:77: don de nyid go zhing rtogs pa des chog pas
NK032(khi)005:80: des chog pa'i don de las bstan du med de /
NK032(khi)005:81: lo kho thag chod cing yid tshim pas na lo zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:82: de ni rtogs pa'i don de gsal 'debs pas shes rab don gyi phyag go //
NK032(khi)005:86: ji ltar chu la chu bzhag dang //
NK032(khi)005:87: ji ltar mar la mar bzhag bzhin //
NK032(khi)005:88: rang gi rang nyid ye shes 'di //
NK032(khi)005:89: legs mthong gang yin 'dir phyag yin //
NK032(khi)005:91: de ni yang dag pa'i mchod brjod do //
NK032(khi)005:92: de yang sangs rgyas phal po che las /
NK032(khi)005:95: sam g+ha'i 'du shes med pa 'di ni yang dag pa'i mchod pa'o zhes bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:96: des na nyid la nyid kyis mchod par brjod pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:97: rang gi sems nyid kyi don la phyag 'tshal ba bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:98: des sngon du mchod par brjod par bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:99: gnyis pa bstan par dam bca' ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:100: chos gzhan gyi lugs kyis bshad par dam bca' ba 'byung ba yin te /
NK032(khi)005:101: gdams ngag 'di'i lugs kyi chos spyi'i 'dod lugs 'chad pa lta bu zhig ma yin te /
NK032(khi)005:102: don rang gi mtshan nyid bla ma'i gdams ngag gis
NK032(khi)005:103: ston pa yin pas na bstan par dam bca' ba'o
NK032(khi)005:104: // de la dang po gdod nas dag pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:105: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs dus gsum du 'du 'bral med /
NK032(khi)005:109: chos bzhi dang ldan pa de la rnam rtog rang
NK032(khi)005:110: rgyud du grub pa rdul tsam gcig kyang mi gnas
NK032(khi)005:111: te / don dam pa blo'i mtha' zab cing phra
NK032(khi)005:112: ba tsam yang mi gnas pas na gdod nas dag
NK032(khi)005:113: te / pa'o // sems nyid kyi don de la
NK032(khi)005:114: bzang rtog dang ngan rtog gi bag chags gang yang
NK032(khi)005:115: mi gnas pas na byang ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:116: snying po'i don de 'khor 'das kun la che chung med par mnyam par khyab pas na chub pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:117: de yang rnam par rtog pa ma yin te /
NK032(khi)005:118: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs yin pas na sems nyid do //
NK032(khi)005:119: kyi zhes bya ba snga ma 'di ni tshig gzhug gcod par byed pas na kyis so //
NK032(khi)005:120: nyid kyi ngo bo zhes pa ni gzhan nas ma
NK032(khi)005:121: yin te rang nyid kyi yin pas na nyid kyi
NK032(khi)005:122: ngo bo'o // snying po'i don de sems nyid dngos
NK032(khi)005:123: po'i gnas lugs kyi ngo bo chos bzhi ldan pa
NK032(khi)005:124: ngo bo'o // de nyid do // kyi zhes bya
NK032(khi)005:125: ba phyi ma 'di gnyis ni tshig gong 'og gnyis
NK032(khi)005:127: don bstan pa ni gzhan zhig nas btsal lam /
NK032(khi)005:132: ston pa lta bu gcig ma yin te /
NK032(khi)005:133: rang la ye nas yod pa'i don ngo ma shes
NK032(khi)005:134: pa de bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gi ngo sprad
NK032(khi)005:135: nas ston pa'o // tshig tu bshad nas /
NK032(khi)005:136: smra ru ma btub pa brjod med kyi don de /
NK032(khi)005:137: tshig med kyi gnas su ngo sprad nas ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:138: de yang smra ru btub pa tsho chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid du gtan la phab nas /
NK032(khi)005:139: smra ru ma btub pa'i don de brdas ngo sprod
NK032(khi)005:140: nas don nyams su myong ba'i don de sangs rgyas
NK032(khi)005:141: kyis gsungs pa'i bka' lung man ngag dang mi 'gal
NK032(khi)005:142: bar sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin nges par yid
NK032(khi)005:143: ches the tshom mi za bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:144: de la dang po chos spyi'i 'dod lugs ni /
NK032(khi)005:145: ston pa gsum gyis bstan pa'i chos yin te /
NK032(khi)005:146: de la chos kyi sku'i ston pa dpal kun tu
NK032(khi)005:147: bzang pos bstan pa'i chos 'chos mdo sde yang snang
NK032(khi)005:149: sde rgyud sde klong sde rnams las gsum ka bstan /
NK032(khi)005:150: de yang don gang la dgongs na /
NK032(khi)005:151: sems can thams cad kyi rgyud la sems bya ba gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)005:152: de yang ma rig pas log par rtogs pa'i 'khrul pa ru 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:153: de yang ma 'khrul bar 'chos par bya ba'i phyir du /
NK032(khi)005:154: gang zag dbang po rab kyi tha ma la 'chos sde ru bskyed pa ma h+aa yo ga bstan /
NK032(khi)005:155: ma 'khrul pa'i don de rgyun chad med par bstan pa'i phyir du /
NK032(khi)005:156: gang zag dbang po rab kyi 'bring la rgyud sde ru lung a nu yo ga bstan /
NK032(khi)005:157: rgyun chad med pa'i don de mi 'dzad cing 'gyur ba med pa'i phyir du /
NK032(khi)005:158: gang zag dbang po rab kyi rab la klong sde ru rdzogs pa a ti yo ga bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:159: de tsho ni gsang sngags nang pa sde gsum yin te /
NK032(khi)005:160: tshul lam thabs ji ltar du bstan na /
NK032(khi)005:161: chos kyi sku dpal ston pa kun tu bzang pos gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:162: 'og min chos kyi dbyings nas byin gyis brlabs nas bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:163: de la longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku yi ston pa dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyis bstan pa'i chos /
NK032(khi)005:164: kri ya yo ga u pa ya gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)005:165: de yang don gang la dgongs na sems can thams
NK032(khi)005:166: cad kyi rgyud la sems pas rtog pa rags su
NK032(khi)005:167: song ba'i lus ngag yid gsum du byung bas lus
NK032(khi)005:168: ngag yid gsum 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru /
NK032(khi)005:169: gang zag dbang po 'bring gi tha ma la lus 'dul phyir kri ya bstan /
NK032(khi)005:170: gang zag dbang po 'bring gi 'bring la ngag 'dul phyir yo ga bstan /
NK032(khi)005:171: gang zag dbang po 'bring gi rab la yid 'dul phyir u pa ya bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:172: de tsho ni gsang sngags phyi pa sde gsum yin te /
NK032(khi)005:173: tshul lam thabs ji ltar du bstan na /
NK032(khi)005:174: longs spyod rdzogs pa'i sku'i ston pa dpal rnam par
NK032(khi)005:175: snang mdzad kyis 'og min 'thug po bkod pa'i zhing
NK032(khi)005:176: khams nas / thams cad rang gi ngo bo sku
NK032(khi)005:177: gsung thugs kyi ngo bo brdas bstan nas bshad pa'o
NK032(khi)005:178: khams nas / // sprul pa sku'i ston pa sh+aakya thub pas bstan pa'i chos /
NK032(khi)005:179: 'dul ba mngon pa mdo sde gsum bstan /
NK032(khi)005:180: de yang don gang la dgongs na sems can thams
NK032(khi)005:181: cad kyi rgyud la lus ngag yid gsum yod pa
NK032(khi)005:182: la brten nas rtog pa rags shing mang du song
NK032(khi)005:183: bas / nyon mongs pa gti mug 'dod chags zhe sdang gsum byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:184: de yang nyon mongs pa gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen
NK032(khi)005:185: po ru gang zag dbang po tha ma'i 'bring la
NK032(khi)005:186: mngon pa bstan / 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen po
NK032(khi)005:187: ru gang zag dbang po tha ma'i tha ma la
NK032(khi)005:189: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru gang zag dbang po tha ma'i rab la mdo sde bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:190: de tsho ni rgyu mtshan nyid kyi sde snod gsum yin te /
NK032(khi)005:191: de yang tshul lam thabs ji ltar du bstan na /
NK032(khi)005:192: sprul pa sku'i ston pa bcom ldan 'das sh+aakya thub pas /
NK032(khi)005:193: rgya gar rdo rje gdan bya rgod phung po'i ri bo du /
NK032(khi)005:194: sku dngos su byon nas sde snod gsum po zhal nas tshig sdeb sbyor legs par gsungs so //
NK032(khi)005:195: de tsho ni dbang po rab 'bring tha ma gsul la dgongs nas /
NK032(khi)005:196: theg pa rim pa dgu ru bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:197: de yang lung mchog bla ma las /
NK032(khi)005:198: nyan thos rang rgyal byang chub sems dpa' gsum //
NK032(khi)005:199: grangs med gsum gyi sangs rgyas sa la slebs //
NK032(khi)005:200: kri ya yo ga u pa ya dang gsum //
NK032(khi)005:201: mi tshe gsum gyi sangs rgyas sa la sbyor //
NK032(khi)005:202: bskyed dang rdzogs dang rdzogs pa chen po gsum //
NK032(khi)005:203: mi tshe gcig gi sangs rgyas lag tu len //
NK032(khi)005:205: gti mug las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)005:206: 'dod chags las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)005:207: zhe sdang las gyur pa nyon mongs pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)005:208: dug gsum spyi mthun las gyur par nyon mongs pa nyi khri chig stong /
NK032(khi)005:209: nyi khri gsum la drug khri /
NK032(khi)005:210: chig stong gsum la sum stong /
NK032(khi)005:211: de'i steng du spyi mthun las gyur pa nyi khri
NK032(khi)005:212: chig stong bsnan pas nyi khri bzhi la brgyad khri
NK032(khi)005:213: / chig stong bzhi la bzhi stong /
NK032(khi)005:214: de ru nyon mongs pa brgyad khri dang bzhi stong du byung ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:215: gti mug 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru mngon pa nyi khri chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:216: 'dod chags 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:217: zhe sdang 'dul ba'i gnyen po ru mdo sde nyi khri chig stong gcig gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:218: 'dod chags zhe sdang gti mug gsum spyi mthun las
NK032(khi)005:219: gyur pa nyi khri dang chig stong gi gnyen po
NK032(khi)005:220: ru / 'dul ba mngon pa mdo sde gsum spyi
NK032(khi)005:221: mthun la gyur pa chos kyi sgo mo nyi khri
NK032(khi)005:223: de ru nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo brgyad khri dang bzhi stong gi gnyen po ru /
NK032(khi)005:224: chos kyi sgo mo brgyad khri dang bzhi stong gcig gsungs pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:225: gnyen po'i don spros pa la dgongs nas gsungs pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:226: gti mug nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen po ru mngon pa nyi khri ching stong gsungs pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:227: 'dod chags nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen po ru 'dul ba nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:228: zhe sdang nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen po ru mdo sde nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:229: dug gsum cha mnyam spyi mthun las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong gi gnyen po ru /
NK032(khi)005:230: sde snod gsum po cha mnyam spyi mthun las gyur pa nyi khri chig stong gsungs pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:232: de yang nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo kha phye bas rten 'brel bcu gnyis su byung ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:244: rga shi dang bcu gnyis su byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:245: de yang chos kyi sgo mo la bye brag tu phye bas gsung rab mdo'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:246: lung du bstan pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:247: tshigs su bcad pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:248: ched du brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:250: rtogs pa brjod pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:252: skyes pa rabs kyi sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:253: shin tu rgyas pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:254: rmad du byung ba'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:255: gtan la dbab pa'i sde dang /
NK032(khi)005:256: dbyangs su bsnyad pa'i sde dang bcu gnyis su bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:257: de ni bye brag tu dbye ba'i don la dgongs te rgyas bsdus 'bring du bka' bstsal lo //
NK032(khi)005:258: de yang nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo bsdus na /
NK032(khi)005:259: ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum du 'dus te /
NK032(khi)005:260: de yang gti mug gi ngo bo ma rig pa ru byung /
NK032(khi)005:261: 'dod chags kyi rang bzhin 'khrul pa ru shar /
NK032(khi)005:262: zhe sdang gi mtshan nyid sdug bsngal du nyams su myong ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:263: rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)005:264: rang gsal dgongs pa'i thugs ma rig /
NK032(khi)005:265: 'dzin pa'i cha la gang gnas kyang //
NK032(khi)005:268: de nas chos kyi sgo mo bsdu na bslab pa gsum du 'dus te /
NK032(khi)005:269: spros pa med pa'i don rig cing gsal bar rtogs pas lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa byung /
NK032(khi)005:270: 'du byed kyi blo med pa'i ngang la tshul bzhin
NK032(khi)005:271: du gnas pas lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa
NK032(khi)005:272: byung / nyon mongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa gang
NK032(khi)005:273: la'ang mi gnas shing chos kyi don dang nam yang
NK032(khi)005:275: lhag pa bsam gtan gyi bslab pa byung ngo //
NK032(khi)005:276: de yang theg pa chen po rgyud bla ma las /
NK032(khi)005:277: spros med rtogs pa shes rab yin //
NK032(khi)005:278: 'du byed med pa tshul khrims yin //
NK032(khi)005:279: gnas med mi 'bral bsam gtan yin //
NK032(khi)005:281: de ni hril gyis bsdu ba'i don la dgongs te nyung la 'dus pa ru bka' stsal to //
NK032(khi)005:282: de yan chad ni chos spyi'i rnam par 'dus pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:283: dper na rdo rje gdan mthong ma myong ba gcig la rdo rje gdan gyi mtshan nyid bshad pas /
NK032(khi)005:284: rdo rje gdan de 'dra gcig yod tshod du 'dug snyam pa las /
NK032(khi)005:285: don lhag ger rtogs pa med pa dang 'dra'o //
NK032(khi)005:286: gnyis pa don rang gi mtshan nyid du nye bar bsdus nas snying po'i don la sbyor ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:287: de yang don rang gi mtshan nyid brjod du med pa'i don de /
NK032(khi)005:288: tshig med pa'i brda ru mtshon nas ston pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:289: de yang dus kyi brda'i dus su gnad kyi brda' bzhis rgyud la sbyar bas /
NK032(khi)005:293: ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa rgyud la 'char bas /
NK032(khi)005:294: gsal ba gnad kyi brdas spros pa med pa'i don de rang gi sems nyid du rig cing /
NK032(khi)005:295: rang gi sems nyid du gsal bar rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)005:296: nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo ma rig pa dag pa ste /
NK032(khi)005:297: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba spros pa med par rtogs pa lhag pa shes rab kyi bslab pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:298: mi rtog pa gnad kyi brdas 'du byed med pa'i
NK032(khi)005:299: don de rang gi sems nyid blo'i rtog pa ci
NK032(khi)005:301: mi rtog pa chos nyid kyi ngang ngam tshul de las mi 'da' ba gcig tu rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)005:302: nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo rtsa ba rang bzhin 'khrul pa chod pa de /
NK032(khi)005:303: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba 'du byed med par gnas pa lhag pa tshul khrims kyi bslab pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:304: bde ba gnad kyi brdas gnas pa med pa mi
NK032(khi)005:305: 'bral ba'i don de rang gi sems nyid lus sems
NK032(khi)005:306: yod du mi tshor ba'i bde ba /
NK032(khi)005:307: nyon mongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa gang la yang mi gnas /
NK032(khi)005:308: chos nyid kyi don dang nam yang mi 'bral bar brtan pa gcig tu rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)005:309: nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang bral ba de /
NK032(khi)005:310: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba gnas pa med par
NK032(khi)005:311: mi 'bral ba lhag pa bsam gtan gyi bslab pa'o
NK032(khi)005:312: // dbyer mi pyed pa gnad kyi brdas chos spyi'i 'dod lugs bslab pa gsum gyi don de /
NK032(khi)005:313: don rang gi mtshan nyid sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs chos bzhi dang ldan pa de /
NK032(khi)005:316: bde ba gsum tshig la tha dad par 'dug kyang /
NK032(khi)005:317: don la ngo bo dbyer mi phyed pa gcig 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:318: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed ces bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:319: mi phyed ces bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi
NK032(khi)005:320: mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa
NK032(khi)005:322: de yang bla mas brdar bstan du byung bas ni chos kyi chos nyid /
NK032(khi)005:323: rang gi rgyud la nyams su myong bas na sems kyi sems nyid /
NK032(khi)005:324: dper na nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu rgya chad phyogs lhung med do //
NK032(khi)005:325: rtog med du lhun gyis grub pa la /
NK032(khi)005:326: blo'i mtha' 'am tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas te /
NK032(khi)005:327: 'du shes dang bral bas nam mkha'i mtshan nyid gnyis
NK032(khi)005:328: gsum gcig tu 'dres pa 'di bzhag phyis mi len
NK032(khi)005:329: gyi dgongs pa / rang rig dang po'i sa ru tshud pa zhes bya'o //
NK032(khi)005:330: de tsa na bsam pa'i blo zad brjod pa'i tshig
NK032(khi)005:331: zad pas chos thams cad kyi tshig don ma lus
NK032(khi)005:334: de yang mdo sangs rgyas thams cad kyi dgongs pa 'dus pa las /
NK032(khi)005:335: ji srid 'du shes yod kyi bar //
NK032(khi)005:336: theg pa'i mtha' la thug pa med //
NK032(khi)005:337: 'du shes med cing gnas med na //
NK032(khi)005:343: don de lta bu go zhing rtogs nas mngon du gyur na sangs rgyas pa rang yin gsungs so //
NK032(khi)005:344: de yang bden nam byas na /
NK032(khi)005:345: man ngag sangs rgyas kyis gsungs pa'i rgyud lung dang mi 'gal bas shes te /
NK032(khi)005:346: de yang rdo rje zam pa'i rtsa ba'i rgyud ye shes gsang ba las /
NK032(khi)005:347: ye nas chos skur gnas pa la //
NK032(khi)005:348: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK032(khi)005:351: ye nas yin pa'i don de rtogs nas rtogs pa
NK032(khi)005:352: brtan pa de la 'bras bur btags zhes bshad do
NK032(khi)005:353: // lung 'phags pa 'da' ka ye shes las /
NK032(khi)005:354: sems ni ye shes 'byung ba'i rgyu //
NK032(khi)005:355: sangs rgyas gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK032(khi)005:357: rgyud sde dang sgrub sde'i don bsdus pa /
NK032(khi)005:358: rna brgyud lung gi phreng ba las /
NK032(khi)005:359: phyogs bcu'i 'jig rten thams cad na //
NK032(khi)005:360: sangs rgyas btsal bas mi rnyed de //
NK032(khi)005:361: rang sems rtogs na sangs rgyas yin //
NK032(khi)005:362: de las gzhan du ma 'tshol cig /
NK032(khi)005:364: dpal dgyes pa rdo rje'i brtag pa gnyis pa las /
NK032(khi)005:365: sems can thams cad sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)005:366: 'on kyang glo bur dri mas bsgribs //
NK032(khi)005:367: dri ma dag na sangs rgyas nyid //
NK032(khi)005:369: glo bur gyi dri ma ni nyon mongs pa'i sgo mo'i rtsa ba /
NK032(khi)005:370: ngo bo rang bzhin mtshan nyid gsum gyis sgrib pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:371: de yang bla ma'i brda dang ngag gis rgyud la sbyar bas /
NK032(khi)005:372: nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo ma rig pa dag /
NK032(khi)005:374: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang bral nas /
NK032(khi)005:375: dri ma dag pa chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba bslab pa gsum gyi don gsal ba /
NK032(khi)005:377: bde pa gsum ngo bo dbyer mi phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:379: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK032(khi)005:380: gnas par dag pa ni sangs rgyas de nyid yin
NK032(khi)005:381: par bshad do // de ni chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don /
NK032(khi)005:382: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de rtogs na /
NK032(khi)005:383: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pas de la tshul bzhin du gnas na /
NK032(khi)005:384: sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gnas pa de rang yin no //
NK032(khi)005:385: de yang mdo sde nges par 'jog pa las /
NK032(khi)005:386: dge sbyong chen pos 'di skad gsungs //
NK032(khi)005:387: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ste //
NK032(khi)005:388: dge ba phun sum tshogs par sbyang //
NK032(khi)005:389: rang gi sems ni yongs su 'dul //
NK032(khi)005:390: 'di ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)005:392: de bas na nyon mongs pa'i rtsa ba ngo bo ma rig pa dag /
NK032(khi)005:394: mtshan nyid sdug bsngal dang bral bas na /
NK032(khi)005:395: sdig pa ci yang mi bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)005:396: chos kyi sgo mo'i rtsa ba bslab pa gsum gyi don gsal ba /
NK032(khi)005:398: bde ba gsum du spyod pas na /
NK032(khi)005:399: dge ba phun sum tshogs par spyad pa yin no //
NK032(khi)005:402: bde ba gsum tshig la tha dad kyang don la ngo bo dbyer mi phyed /
NK032(khi)005:403: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:404: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)005:405: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pas na /
NK032(khi)005:406: rang gi sems nyid blo'i rtog pa la mi gnas par thul /
NK032(khi)005:407: sems nyid don dam pa blo'i spyod yul du ma
NK032(khi)005:408: gyur pa de sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin pas
NK032(khi)005:409: / de bla ma'i brda' dang ngag gis smra ru btub pa tshig tu bshad /
NK032(khi)005:410: smra ru ma btub pa'i don brdas ngo sprad nas bstan pa de /
NK032(khi)005:411: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa bstan pa yin pas na /
NK032(khi)005:412: de ni sangs rgyas bstan pa yin //
NK032(khi)005:414: don de la gnas na sangs rgyas kyi bstan pa la gnas pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:415: de yan chad kyis gang thal na sngon du mchod
NK032(khi)005:416: par brjod cing bstan pa dam bca' ba'i skabs thal
NK032(khi)005:417: lo // de yang gang zag dbang po rab kyis chos zab mo'i mtshan thos pa'am /
NK032(khi)005:419: bstan par dam bca' ba tsam gyis grol ba yang yod /
NK032(khi)005:420: gang zag dbang po 'bring gis gzhung thos pa tsam gyis grol ba yang yod /
NK032(khi)005:421: gang zag dbang po tha ma la zhib tshags 'bru
NK032(khi)005:422: bsnon dpe don man ngag dang mi 'gal bar ston
NK032(khi)005:423: dgos pa yang yod pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:424: de la dang po gdams ngag 'dis mtshon pa'am /
NK032(khi)005:426: bstan par dam bca' ba tsam gyis ma grol na //
NK032(khi)005:427: gnyis pa gdams ngag rdo rje zam pa 'di'i gzhung ston pa la gsum ste /
NK032(khi)005:428: gong du chos spyi dang rang gi mtshan nyid kyi don /
NK032(khi)005:429: sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs nyid kyi ngo bo nyid kyi don bstan pa de /
NK032(khi)005:430: sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yin nges par ston pa ni //
NK032(khi)005:431: don dang po sangs rgyas pa yin nges par gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus dang gcig /
NK032(khi)005:432: bar du gtan la phebs pa'i dus dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)005:433: tha ma nyams su shar ba'i dus dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)005:435: chang mig gis mthong ba dang /
NK032(khi)005:436: ro zhim pa ru shes pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:437: gzi bas nang rtags phyi ru shar ba dang 'dra'o //
NK032(khi)005:438: don dang po gtan la 'bebs pa'i dus la gsum ste /
NK032(khi)005:439: rna brgyud lung gi gter chen 'grol ba dang gcig /
NK032(khi)005:440: sgom med don gyi gzer chen gdab pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)005:441: re dogs med pas dbyings la gtad pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)005:442: bar du gtan la phebs pa'i dus la yang gsum ste /
NK032(khi)005:443: dbang ngang gis rdzogs pas sgom sgrub dge ba'i chos
NK032(khi)005:444: la mi ltos par gtan la phebs pa dang gcig
NK032(khi)005:445: / sku rang chas su gyur pas gnyis 'dzin las grol bar gtan la phebs pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)005:446: don gcig tu rtogs pas rtog dpyod las 'das par gtan la phebs pa dang gsum mo //
NK032(khi)005:447: tha ma nyams su shar ba'i dus la yang gsum ste /
NK032(khi)005:448: 'di ni rdo rje'i lam mchog ste //
NK032(khi)005:450: skal ldan 'bad pa med par grol //
NK032(khi)005:452: grol ba rang byung gzhan las min //
NK032(khi)005:454: deng mchod par brjod cing bstan par dam bca' ba la tshig rkang gnyis /
NK032(khi)005:455: gdams ngag gi gzhung gi rtsa ba la tshig rkang dgu ste /
NK032(khi)005:456: bcu gcig tu bstan pa'i gzhung de thos pa tsam gyis grol na /
NK032(khi)005:457: gang zag dbang po tha ma la 'bru bsnol zhib tshags sam /
NK032(khi)005:458: dpe gcig don gcig man ngag gis bka' lung dang mi 'gal bar /
NK032(khi)005:459: yid ches the tshom mi za bar ston pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:460: de la dang po rna brgyud lung gi gter chen dgrol ba la /
NK032(khi)005:463: go ba ni don mdor bsdus pa yin la /
NK032(khi)005:464: tshig ni de'i don rgyas par bshad pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:465: de yang dang po go ba la rna brgyud ces pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:466: gang zag gi snyan nas snyan du brgyud pa rnams so //
NK032(khi)005:468: rig 'dzin pa barda'am lung bstan pa tsam gyis grol ba rnams so //
NK032(khi)005:469: de yang dang po rna brgyud sngon la yong ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:470: rang la drin che ba'i bla ma gong mas snyan nas rna ba ru brgyud nas ston pa'am /
NK032(khi)005:471: tshig sdeb sbyor legs par bya ba'i phyir du bstan pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:474: barda'am lung bstan pa tsam gyis grol ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:475: gter chen dgrol ba zhes pa go ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:476: dbul 'phongs su gyur pas gter rnyed pa'i dpes mtshon pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:477: de yang rgya gar gyi yul sing+gala bya ba na /
NK032(khi)005:478: yab tshong dpon phyi'i rgya mtsho la nor bu len pa'i rigs gcig gis /
NK032(khi)005:479: phyi rabs la phan pa srid snyam nas /
NK032(khi)005:480: sgyed po ma sgyed mi sgul ba de'i 'og tu gser phye bum pa gang sbas nas bzhag pas /
NK032(khi)005:481: dus lan gcig tshong dpon de grongs nas /
NK032(khi)005:482: bza' mi de min tsho zad pa'i lhag ma /
NK032(khi)005:483: bu mo ltog ma gcig lus nas yod pa la /
NK032(khi)005:484: yul gcig na gter sa'i dpyad shes pa'i mi sa
NK032(khi)005:485: 'og sa steng sa bla gsum na gter ram nor
NK032(khi)005:486: ci yod pa mthong ba gcig yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:487: lan cig sing+ga la'i yul de ru brtol nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:488: dbul mo bza' ba dang gyon pa ci yang med /
NK032(khi)005:489: nor du ras gos hrul po gcig las med pa /
NK032(khi)005:490: de yang nyin mo smad du dkris nas 'tsho ba bya 'tshol byi'u 'tshol byed do //
NK032(khi)005:491: nang lto nang 'tshol nub lto nub 'tshol ba /
NK032(khi)005:492: nub mo ras gos de gnyis lteb gcig byas nas
NK032(khi)005:493: bshul du bkab nas nyal ba las gzhan ci yang
NK032(khi)005:494: med pa'i dbul mo de'i sgyed po ma sgyed de'i
NK032(khi)005:495: 'og na / phas gter du sbas pa'i gser bum pa gang 'dug pa de mthong nas /
NK032(khi)005:496: gter sa'i dpyad shes pa'i mi des /
NK032(khi)005:497: dbul mo de'i drung du phyin nas /
NK032(khi)005:498: dbul mo khyed la bza' ba dang /
NK032(khi)005:499: gyon pa ci yang med dam zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:500: mo na re khyed ci 'dod pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:501: nga la ni ci yang med do zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:502: gter sa'i dpyad shes pa'i mi des /
NK032(khi)005:503: dbul mo de'i drung du phyin nas /
NK032(khi)005:504: khyed rang gi sgyed po ma sgyed kyi 'og na /
NK032(khi)005:505: yab kyis sbas pa'i gser bum pa gang 'dug gi /
NK032(khi)005:506: de khyed rang thon la bde bar longs spyod dang /
NK032(khi)005:507: gzhan su la yang rag ma lus par yod cing byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:509: cang bden nam bden na dang dga' ste /
NK032(khi)005:510: nga bya ba bsod nams chung bas yod shes kyang ngas mi rnyed byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:511: rnyed 'ong zhing de thon la bde bar longs spyod cig byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:512: gal te bden nam snyam nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:513: sgyed po ma sgyed kyi 'og nas gser phye bum
NK032(khi)005:514: pa gang rnyed nas de la mos cha gsum du
NK032(khi)005:515: bgos nas / cha gcig bla ma dang dkon mchog la mchod pa'i phud du bcad /
NK032(khi)005:516: cha gcig long sprang dang yul de'i rgyal po la khral dang sbyin par bcad /
NK032(khi)005:517: dus de tsa na rgyal po blas 'tsho ba bya ba /
NK032(khi)005:518: so nam bya mi dgos par khral gyis 'tsho ba yin skad /
NK032(khi)005:519: mnga' bdag dpal 'khor btsan bzhugs pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)005:520: rgyal po'i sras gcig gis yar klungs rog pa rtsa ru byon pas /
NK032(khi)005:521: rgan mo gcig gis nas phung gcig la bzang ngan gsum du phye nas 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:522: rgyal bu des nas tshan pa gsum du 'byed pa ci tsug yin byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:524: nas kyi snying po bzang shos 'di /
NK032(khi)005:525: bla ma dang dkon mchog gnyan pas mchod pa'i phud du bcad pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:526: 'bring po ni nged rang gis so nam dka' bas byas pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:528: ngan shos 'di rgyal po dang long sprang la khral
NK032(khi)005:529: du 'jal ba dang sbyin par gtong ba byed pa
NK032(khi)005:530: yin zer bas / de ru rgyal bu de pho brang du byon nas /
NK032(khi)005:531: nged rang rgyal po kun so nam byed dgos par 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:532: rgyal po'i dpya dang long sprang gi yon la nas ngan shos ster ba yin 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:533: nged rgyal po dang long sprang mnyam por byed pa 'dug zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:534: de nas bod kyi rgyal po so nam la tshud pa lags skad /
NK032(khi)005:535: rgya gar na da lta yang rgyal po blas 'tsho ba yod pa yin skad do //
NK032(khi)005:536: de yang dbul mos gter rnyed pa des yar bla ma dang dkon mchog la mchod pa /
NK032(khi)005:537: mar rgyal po dang long sprang dpya 'bul zhing sbyin pa gtong ba /
NK032(khi)005:538: bar mo rang gi bza' gos la sogs pa phun sum tshogs pa la longs spyod du byung bas /
NK032(khi)005:539: gzhan la rag ma lus pa'i dpe de bzhin no //
NK032(khi)005:540: gdams ngag 'di rang gi brgyud pa'i bla ma rnams
NK032(khi)005:541: kyis ye nas bde bar gshegs pa'i snying po rang
NK032(khi)005:542: gi rgyud la yod pa'i sems nyid ma nor zhing
NK032(khi)005:543: 'khrul pa med pa'i gter chen po de bla ma'i
NK032(khi)005:544: brda dang ngag la brten nas /
NK032(khi)005:545: ma rig pas gter sgo bsdams pa de bkral bas /
NK032(khi)005:546: gter chen po gser bum pa gang yod de rnyed
NK032(khi)005:547: pas dbul mos yar la mchod rgyu byung ba bzhin
NK032(khi)005:548: du / sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa lon /
NK032(khi)005:549: mar la sbyin rgyu byung ba dang 'dra bar /
NK032(khi)005:550: sems can la thugs rjes skyob /
NK032(khi)005:551: rang nyid phun sum tshogs pa la longs spyod du byung ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:552: don rang gi sems nyid rtogs pas /
NK032(khi)005:553: gzung 'dzin gyi rnam par rtog pa dang bral nas /
NK032(khi)005:554: 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol te /
NK032(khi)005:555: chos nyid la longs spyad du byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:556: de tsa na thar pa gzhan la rag ma lus te /
NK032(khi)005:557: sangs rgyas kho na rang nyid do //
NK032(khi)005:558: de ni gter chen grol ba'i go ba dbul mos gter rnyed pa'i dpes mtshon pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:559: gter chen dgrol ba'i tshig la gnyis te /
NK032(khi)005:560: rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:561: gang zag gdams ngag gis grol ba'i brgyud pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:562: dang po rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa la'ang go ba dang /
NK032(khi)005:564: rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i go ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:565: dang po rig 'dzin zhes pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:566: 'bras bu gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i rigs rgyud 'dzin pa yin la /
NK032(khi)005:567: brdas grol ba ni tshig mang po bshad ma dgos te /
NK032(khi)005:568: bla ma gong mas brda' bstan pa tsam gyis grol ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:569: brgyud pa ni rdo rje sems dpa' nas /
NK032(khi)005:570: bee ro tsa na yan chad du /
NK032(khi)005:571: gcig nas gcig tu phreng ma chad par brgyud pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:572: de yang tshul lam thabs ji ltar du brgyud na /
NK032(khi)005:573: de la gtam rgyud 'di byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:574: dang po chos 'di 'byung ba'i khungs ni /
NK032(khi)005:575: rgya gar gyi yul yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:576: rgya gar yul de na gling chen po dgu yod de /
NK032(khi)005:577: de yang shar phyogs na b+hang+ga la'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:578: lho phyogs na b+he ta la'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:579: nub phyogs na o rgyan gyi gling /
NK032(khi)005:580: byang phyogs na kha che'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:581: shar lho mtshams na khams bu'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:582: lho nub mtshams na zangs gling /
NK032(khi)005:583: nub byang mtshams na za hor gyi gling /
NK032(khi)005:584: byang shar mtshams na ka ma ru pa'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:585: dbus na rgya gar rdo rje gdan dang dgu yod pa las /
NK032(khi)005:586: gling de tsho las chos 'di 'byung ba'i gnas ni nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul yin no //
NK032(khi)005:587: de la spyir rgya gar gyi yul na chos skyong
NK032(khi)005:588: ba'i rgyal po'i rigs d+har+m+aa r+aa dza bya ba dang
NK032(khi)005:589: / srid skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs u pa r+aa dza bya ba gnyis yod pa las /
NK032(khi)005:590: chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs de gcig skyes gnyis skyes d+harma r+aa dza bya ba ru 'ong ste /
NK032(khi)005:591: de yang las dge ba'i las min pa sdig pa'i las yid la mi 'gyu /
NK032(khi)005:594: byas na chos skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rgyal srid mi zin no //
NK032(khi)005:595: srid skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rigs de gcig skyes gnyis
NK032(khi)005:596: skyes thams cad u pa r+aa dza bya ba ru
NK032(khi)005:597: yong skad / de la las dmag dang sdig pa'i
NK032(khi)005:598: las min pa dge ba'i las yid la bya yang
NK032(khi)005:599: yong skad / mi 'gyu / byed kyang mi byed /
NK032(khi)005:601: byas na srid skyong ba'i rgyal po'i rgyal sa mi zin pa yin skad do //
NK032(khi)005:602: de yang chos skyong ba'i rgyal po dri med gtsug
NK032(khi)005:603: phud sh+aaka bzang gi rigs mtshan dri med gtsug phud
NK032(khi)005:604: sh+aaka bzang bya ba'i btsun mo dam pa bya ba
NK032(khi)005:605: la sras mo mtshar sdug 'od du 'bar ba /
NK032(khi)005:606: mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa /
NK032(khi)005:607: 'gro bas blta ba'i 'os su gyur pas /
NK032(khi)005:608: bltas pas chog mi shes pa gcig sku 'khrungs te /
NK032(khi)005:610: nga'i sras mo 'di 'gro ba gzhan la bstan par phangs zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:611: pho brang dgu thog gi rtse la 'tsho ba'i ma ma dang bcas pa bzhugs su bcug go //
NK032(khi)005:612: de'i dus de'i tshe chos skyong ba'i rgyal po de
NK032(khi)005:613: la rgyal bu med pas gdung brgyud chad 'gro bar
NK032(khi)005:614: 'dug ste / de'i dus su chos kyi sku'i chos kyi sku dpal bde ba chen po /
NK032(khi)005:615: chos kyi sku'i longs spyod rdzogs sku dpal kun tu bzang po /
NK032(khi)005:616: chos kyi sku'i sprul pa'i sku dpal rdo rje sems dpa' /
NK032(khi)005:619: sku sprul pa'i sku yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:620: rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs rnam par dag pa'i ngang nas /
NK032(khi)005:621: thugs rjes 'gro ba'i don du 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi don ston par sprul pa bkye ba /
NK032(khi)005:622: sems dag pa lha'i bu zhes bya ba de /
NK032(khi)005:623: 'og min lha'i gnas na bzhugs pa'i tshe /
NK032(khi)005:624: lha'i dbang po brgya byin gyis mkhyen nas /
NK032(khi)005:625: lha'i bu sems dag pa khyed ni bcom ldan 'das
NK032(khi)005:626: rdo rje sems dpas 'gro ba mi'i yul du 'bras
NK032(khi)005:627: bu gsang sngags kyi chos ston par sprul pa yin
NK032(khi)005:628: pas / zhes dran pa bskul bas de ru sems
NK032(khi)005:629: dag pa lha'i bus rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa
NK032(khi)005:630: yin par rang ngo rang gis shes nas /
NK032(khi)005:631: lho 'dzam bu'i gling du chos skyong ba'i rgyal po
NK032(khi)005:632: dri med gtsug phud sh+aaka bzang gi gdung gsob pa
NK032(khi)005:633: la / sras mo mdzes ma dang ldan pa'i lhums su zhugs pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:634: de yang zam pa chen po dbang gi man ngag las /
NK032(khi)005:635: yang sprul dga' rab rdo rje de //
NK032(khi)005:636: 'dzam bu'i gling du rgyal thebs byon //
NK032(khi)005:638: de yang ji ltar du byon na /
NK032(khi)005:642: zla ba nya'i gdugs nyi ma rtse shar la /
NK032(khi)005:643: sras mo mdzes ma dang ldan pa'i drung du /
NK032(khi)005:644: bya g.yu bya khu byug gcig tu sku sprul nas /
NK032(khi)005:645: ku khug ku khug pa lan gsum du skad bton nas song ste /
NK032(khi)005:646: nga do nub 'ong ngo bya ba'i brdar byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:647: do nub srod la khye'u chung mtshar sdug 'od du
NK032(khi)005:648: 'bar ba gcig mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa
NK032(khi)005:649: 'gro bas blta ba'i 'os su gyur pa /
NK032(khi)005:650: bltas pas chog mi shes pa /
NK032(khi)005:653: dbu skra le'u ru 'grol ba gcig byung nas /
NK032(khi)005:655: nangs par tho rangs khar nam mkha' la sku gshegs nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:656: de nas sang phod de'i dus tshod du sras mo de la /
NK032(khi)005:657: sras po mtshan dang ldan pa dpe byad dang ldan pa gcig 'khrungs te /
NK032(khi)005:658: yab la ngo tsha nas lo bdun gyi bar du gsang ngo //
NK032(khi)005:659: de nas sras mo des rgyal po de la /
NK032(khi)005:660: nga la sras 'di lta bu gcig mnga' na byas nas bstan pas /
NK032(khi)005:661: der yab rgyal pos de la mtshan bltas nas /
NK032(khi)005:662: de'i 'phro la ling gis brgyal nas 'dug go //
NK032(khi)005:663: de nas yab de brgyal sangs tsa na sras mo
NK032(khi)005:664: des yab rgyal po la ma mnyes sam byas pas
NK032(khi)005:666: nga mi dga' ba ci mchi /
NK032(khi)005:667: khyod kyi bu 'di rigs byed lha'i sprul pa gcig 'dug pa /
NK032(khi)005:668: rigs ni theg pa chen po'i rigs byed pa mdzes shing yab mi mnga' bas na /
NK032(khi)005:670: 'di'i drin las theg pa chen po'i chos skad cig
NK032(khi)005:671: mas don rtogs nas tshe da res gcig pus sangs
NK032(khi)005:672: rgya ba'i chos zab mo gcig dar 'ong bar 'dug
NK032(khi)005:673: pa la / nga rgas pas spyan chab shar gyis byung ba yin skad /
NK032(khi)005:674: spyan chab byung yang bu de la dga' ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:675: sras mo mi nongs par rab tu song ste /
NK032(khi)005:676: bu rdo rje sems dpa'i yang sprul yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:677: de bas na dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya ba ru mtshan btags so //
NK032(khi)005:678: de nas dga' rab rdo rjes lo brgyad lon tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:679: yum 'di ru bde bar bzhugs shig /
NK032(khi)005:680: 'di nas nub phyogs o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:683: me tog u dum wa ra'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:684: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya ba na /
NK032(khi)005:685: sgrub pa'i gnas gser gyi brag phug yu ba can yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:686: nga de ru sgrub pa la 'gro /
NK032(khi)005:687: dus da res kyi mi lus 'di la dam pa'i chos gcig ma 'grub na /
NK032(khi)005:688: 'jig rten 'di'i rgyal srid btsan yang nub gcig gi
NK032(khi)005:689: rmi lam tsam las med pas de dus su mi
NK032(khi)005:691: yum la phyag btsal zhu ba byas nas brag phug yu ba can du sgrub pa la gshegs so //
NK032(khi)005:692: de nas yang glang gi lo zla ba dpyid ra ba /
NK032(khi)005:694: zla ba nya'i gdugs par nyi ma'i zer la /
NK032(khi)005:695: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sku gsung thugs
NK032(khi)005:696: gsum rnam par dag pa'i sprul pa sems dag pa
NK032(khi)005:697: lha'i bu zhes bya ba snang ba'i gzugs su grub
NK032(khi)005:698: la / reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa /
NK032(khi)005:699: 'od kyi lus can la mtshan dang dpe byad kyis brgyan pa /
NK032(khi)005:700: sku gcer bu dbu skra le'u 'grol ba la pa ti sngon po'i sham thabs gsol ba /
NK032(khi)005:701: phyag g.yas na gser gyi rdo rje bsnams pa /
NK032(khi)005:702: g.yon na shel gyi dril bu dku la brten pa /
NK032(khi)005:703: de lta bu gcig gis phyag g.yas pa'i rdo rje dga' rab rdo rje'i spyi bo ru bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)005:705: a ha ho 'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:710: don de dbyer phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:711: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)005:712: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK032(khi)005:713: gnas pa'i chos nyid kyi rang sgra zhag bdun gyi
NK032(khi)005:714: bar du ma yal bar ting nge 'dzin thun gcig
NK032(khi)005:716: a ha bya ba ni skye 'gags med bya ba yin la /
NK032(khi)005:717: ho'i bya ba de gnyis med dbyer mi phyed pa'i
NK032(khi)005:718: don de thugs khar phebs bya ba yin gsung ngo
NK032(khi)005:719: // ting nge 'dzin de las bzhengs tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:721: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs de /
NK032(khi)005:723: mun khung du sgron me btegs pa bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:724: byas pa dang bcos pa med par /
NK032(khi)005:725: rang gsal du lhag gis rgyud la shar zhing rtogs so //
NK032(khi)005:726: don de mi brjed mi yal bar bya ba'i brjed rdo ru /
NK032(khi)005:727: sems dag lha'i bus a wan d+ha ra zhes brda' bstan pas /
NK032(khi)005:728: bod kyi skad du khyed rang nam mkha' dag pa
NK032(khi)005:729: la 'ja' gsal ba 'di la ltos dang byas pa'i
NK032(khi)005:731: mdun gyi nam mkha' dag pa'i dkyil na 'ja' gcig
NK032(khi)005:732: shar nas 'dug pa de la dga' rab rdo rjes
NK032(khi)005:733: bltas pas / nam mkha' dag pa de dmigs su med pa chos dbyings kyi brda' /
NK032(khi)005:734: 'ja' kha dog lnga dang gsal bar ldan pa de
NK032(khi)005:735: dmigs med kyi don de ma 'gags par rig cing
NK032(khi)005:736: gsal ba ye shes kyi brda' /
NK032(khi)005:737: de nyid tha dad du ma song ste dbyer mi phyed de /
NK032(khi)005:738: dbyings ye shes gnyis su med pa'i brda' /
NK032(khi)005:739: sems dag lha'i bu'am 'ja' gsal ba de snang ba'i
NK032(khi)005:740: gzugs su ma 'gags par gsal ba de mtshon par
NK032(khi)005:742: reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa de dmigs su med pa shes rab kyi brda' /
NK032(khi)005:743: de gnyis tha dad du ma song ste /
NK032(khi)005:744: ngo bo dbyer med gcig tu 'dug pa de thabs dang shes rab gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)005:745: dbyings dang ye shes gnyis su med pa /
NK032(khi)005:746: don sems nyid dngos po'i gnas lugs chos bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK032(khi)005:747: nam mkha' dag pa la 'ja' gsal ba lta bu gcig rtogs so //
NK032(khi)005:748: der zhing las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo 'bar ma'i gdong can dang /
NK032(khi)005:749: las las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo mkha' la gshegs ma dang /
NK032(khi)005:750: sngags las skyes pa'i mkha' 'gro ma'i gtso mo mkha'
NK032(khi)005:751: la spyod ma dang gsum yang mdun du shar gyis
NK032(khi)005:752: byung nas / dga' rab rdo rje la chos zab
NK032(khi)005:753: mo 'di lta bu'i bka' skyong ba'i chos skyong nged
NK032(khi)005:755: 'di bsgrub cing bsrung ba la dngos grub ster /
NK032(khi)005:756: nyams su mi len cing dam tshig mi bsrung ba
NK032(khi)005:757: la bka'i chad pa gcod pa yin no gsungs nas
NK032(khi)005:758: / dga' rab rdo rje la byin gyis kyang brlabs /
NK032(khi)005:760: gzhan gyis ma bcol nyid kyis zhal bzhes ma bya
NK032(khi)005:761: ba yin pas rang dam rang gis bcas pa'i bka'
NK032(khi)005:762: skyong gi mkha' 'gro sde gsum bya ba byin rlabs
NK032(khi)005:763: dang nus mthu shin tu che ba yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:764: chos 'di gnyan pa yin pas dam tshig shin tu gtsang dgos pa lags skad do //
NK032(khi)005:765: de yang sems dag lha'i bus slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje la bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs //
NK032(khi)005:766: rtogs pa tsam gyis don mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)005:767: sgrib pa la sbyangs dka' ba nyon mongs pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:768: shes bya'i sgrib pa de nyid du dag /
NK032(khi)005:769: thob pa la dka' ba thun mong gi dngos grub
NK032(khi)005:770: dang mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob ste
NK032(khi)005:771: / dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na phub sog zhor la byung ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:772: yang na nor bu rin po che sngon la rnyed
NK032(khi)005:773: pa de la gsol ba btab na dgos 'dod 'phral
NK032(khi)005:774: la 'byung ba lta bur gyur pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:775: de ni slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i lo rgyus so //
NK032(khi)005:776: de nas slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes 'gro ba'i don du byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:777: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi thugs la dad pa rang bzhin gyis shar te /
NK032(khi)005:779: nyi ma la nye ring gi rtog pa med kyang /
NK032(khi)005:780: snod bcud gtsang ma'i nang du 'char ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:782: ga re bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)005:783: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang /
NK032(khi)005:784: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis nas 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)005:785: de'i gong du grol ba'i thabs mi 'dug bas /
NK032(khi)005:786: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs
NK032(khi)005:787: rgya ba'i chos gcig yod du gsha' bar 'dug pa
NK032(khi)005:788: la / de yang gzhan na dri ba'i kha na med de /
NK032(khi)005:789: grong khyer ser skya'i sgo kha dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na /
NK032(khi)005:790: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya /
NK032(khi)005:791: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya bzhugs pas /
NK032(khi)005:792: de lta bu'i chos gcig yod na de ru khung
NK032(khi)005:793: chod yong sems nas phyogs der rgyu mtshan nyid kyi
NK032(khi)005:794: pan+di ta la spyan g.yas pas gzigs /
NK032(khi)005:795: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta la spyan g.yon pas gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)005:797: bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)005:798: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib par sbyangs kyang /
NK032(khi)005:799: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)005:800: de'i gong du grol ba'i thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:801: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:802: tshe da res gcig pus sangs rgya ba'i chos gcig yod du gsha' bar 'dug pa las /
NK032(khi)005:803: de lta bu gcig med na de ring sang dus
NK032(khi)005:804: btab pa'i mi yang stabs kha en res 'dzol nas
NK032(khi)005:806: lan gcig ci tshugs su 'gro rang ci cha byas nas dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:807: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta rnams ci yang mi gsung /
NK032(khi)005:808: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams spyan zur gyis brdas bskul nas /
NK032(khi)005:809: mig log byas 'og ma dag des lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)005:810: de lta bu shes pa 'o skol gyi 'di na med /
NK032(khi)005:811: 'di nas nub phyogs su phyin pa na /
NK032(khi)005:812: dpal o rgyan gyi yul d+ha na ko sha'i gling phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po'i 'gram /
NK032(khi)005:813: me tog u dum wa ra 'byung ba'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:815: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya
NK032(khi)005:816: ba na bsgrub pa'i gnas gser gyi brag phug yu
NK032(khi)005:817: ba can bya ba yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:818: de na rigs byed lha'i sprul pa slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje zhes bya ba zhugs te /
NK032(khi)005:819: de la bcom ldan 'das dpal rdo rje sems dpa'i
NK032(khi)005:820: sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu zhes bya bas byin
NK032(khi)005:821: gyis brlabs nas / skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas
NK032(khi)005:822: tshe gcig gi 'tshang rgya ba'i chos khong la yod
NK032(khi)005:823: pa yin pas de ru phyin na yong /
NK032(khi)005:824: gzhan gang na yang de lta bu'i chos shes pa med zer skad /
NK032(khi)005:825: de yang nub phyogs zhes pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:826: rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi nub phyogs yin te /
NK032(khi)005:827: yang na nyon mongs pa'i rnam par rtog pa mi skye bar nub 'gro bas na nub phyogs so //
NK032(khi)005:828: dpal o rgyan gyi yul ni /
NK032(khi)005:829: de la dpal ni rtogs pa bdag gi dpal dang /
NK032(khi)005:830: thugs rje gzhan gyi dpal lo //
NK032(khi)005:831: yang na pho skyes dpa' bor gyur la mo skyes dpa' mo ru 'byung ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:832: u rgyan gyi yul ni me tog u dum wa ras brgyan pa'i yul yin la /
NK032(khi)005:833: yang na gnas gzhan las khyad par 'phags te /
NK032(khi)005:834: dpa' bo dang dpa' mo rang bzhin gyis 'byung ba'i gnas yin pas o rgyan dang 'dra ste /
NK032(khi)005:835: kun gyi spyi bor khur ba'i 'os su gyur pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:836: d+ha na ko sha'i gling ni /
NK032(khi)005:837: d+ha na sems ngal bso ba /
NK032(khi)005:838: ko sha ni yid skyob par byed pa /
NK032(khi)005:839: gling ni sems ma bcos par gnas pa zhig 'ong ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:840: phyi'i rgya mtsho chen po ni chu ba tsh+wa can btung du mi btub pa /
NK032(khi)005:841: 'gram zhes pa ni rgya mtsho de'i chu 'gram la yar nas yar la /
NK032(khi)005:842: ro mchog bde ba'i tshal ni /
NK032(khi)005:843: bza' shing gi nags dang tshal yod de /
NK032(khi)005:844: de dag zos pa'i ro mchog gis rgyud la zag pa med pa'i bde ba bskyed nus pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:845: de ltar phyi rim na yar la me tog u
NK032(khi)005:846: dum wa ra mthing ga sha stag 'byung ba'i gling
NK032(khi)005:847: chags pa'o // de lho phyogs yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:848: mthing ga de'i mdangs ri rab la phog /
NK032(khi)005:849: ri rab kyi mdangs rgya mtsho la phog /
NK032(khi)005:850: rgya mtsho'i mdangs nam mkha' la phog pas /
NK032(khi)005:851: lho 'dzam bu'i gling pa'i nam mkha' mthing kha de bzhin du lags skad /
NK032(khi)005:853: chos can gyi rnam par rtog pa thams cad chos nyid kyi ngang du thim pas dur /
NK032(khi)005:854: khrod ni rig pa'i ye shes skye 'gags med par gnas pa'i khrod /
NK032(khi)005:856: gser gyi gling nas rdo gzhan mi 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:857: dur khrod chen po gser gling de ru tha mal gyi rtog pa rang rgyud pa mi skye ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:859: chos nyid gnyis su med pa'i don la dgyes pa chen po phyogs ris med pa /
NK032(khi)005:860: de gnyis su med par chos kyi dbyings su khyab par brdal ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:862: mchog dang thun mong gi dngos grub thams cad 'grub cing thob par byed pa'i gnas so //
NK032(khi)005:863: gser gyi brag zhes pa ni /
NK032(khi)005:864: chos nyid gser bzhin du rkyen gyis mi 'gyur ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:866: zab mo'i don dmigs su med pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:868: chos nyid zab mo'i don 'gyur ba med pa rdo rje lta bu de rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:869: grub thob phreng ba ma chad par yu ba bzhin du breng nger yong ba la zer ba'o //
NK032(khi)005:870: 'o na de lta bu'i gnas mtshan nyid dang ldan
NK032(khi)005:871: pa de ru 'gro ba la dka' sla dang nye
NK032(khi)005:872: ring ji tsam yod ces dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:873: dka' sla ni shin tu dka' ste /
NK032(khi)005:874: mi med pa'i lung stong la zla ba bcu gsum du 'gro dgos te /
NK032(khi)005:875: lam na gcan gzan ma rung pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:877: mi dang mi ma yin dang lha ma yin la sogs pa yod /
NK032(khi)005:878: gcan gzan gdug pa gcan dang 'phrad na khrum gyis zos nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)005:879: sbrul gdug pa can dang 'phrad na dug sbrul gyi lce yug byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:880: snag ma tsho kha ru sibs la /
NK032(khi)005:881: rus pa tsho thang la dkar spungs kyis 'gro /
NK032(khi)005:882: mi ma yin dang 'phrad na khyur gyis mid nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)005:883: lha ma yin dang 'phrad na skad lhang gi bton
NK032(khi)005:884: pa tsam gyis mig khrag 'phrul gyis 'chi ba yong
NK032(khi)005:885: / dka' sla nye ring de tsam du med na nged kyang 'gro ste gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)005:886: de ru slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi thugs
NK032(khi)005:887: la ga re nga'i lus 'di la khong gis bsad
NK032(khi)005:888: nas shi yang sems ni slob dpon dga' rab rdo
NK032(khi)005:889: rje'i gam du ci brtol cig byed dgos /
NK032(khi)005:890: slob dpon gyi thugs kyis mkhyen nas nga'i sems la byin gyis brlab tu 'ong bas /
NK032(khi)005:891: sems 'khor ba ru gtan du ma 'khyams na /
NK032(khi)005:892: lus da res gcig po la shi dang ma shi med kyi sems nas /
NK032(khi)005:893: the tshom ma zos par gshegs pas /
NK032(khi)005:894: zla ba ril po bcu gsum na ri brag gcig tu brtol te /
NK032(khi)005:895: btsun pa hral po phyag na mda' lnga dang gzhu gcig bsnams pa /
NK032(khi)005:896: sham thabs thod du bcing ba gcig dang 'phrad de /
NK032(khi)005:897: ga re gzhan 'di ru su yang yong ba'i don med de /
NK032(khi)005:898: slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje yin pa las 'os
NK032(khi)005:899: med gcig sems nas slob dpon la gser gyi man+dala
NK032(khi)005:900: phul ba la / chag chag 'debs pa'i chu ma rnyed pas /
NK032(khi)005:902: khyod rang la lus 'dug pa la gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)005:903: de ru ga re nga la lus yod /
NK032(khi)005:905: rtsa la khrag yod sems nas /
NK032(khi)005:906: lus la gtar kha byas su btub pa'i rtsa tsho spu gri ka ma las gshags nas /
NK032(khi)005:907: man+dala bshams pa la khrag gis chag chag btab /
NK032(khi)005:908: gser gyi tshom bu bkod nas /
NK032(khi)005:910: bskor ba lan mang po byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:912: khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu 'tshal zhes gsol ba btab pas /
NK032(khi)005:913: ci yang mi gsung bar dur khrod chen po de ru gshegs nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:914: de'i phyir 'brangs nas phyag dang bskor ba nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du byas /
NK032(khi)005:915: zla ba ngo re la zhu ba'i don re phul kyang ci yang mi gsung nas /
NK032(khi)005:916: da 'o skol la gdams ngag mi gnang bar 'dug
NK032(khi)005:917: pas yul du phyin na ni lus la yang bar
NK032(khi)005:918: chad yong ste / sems kyang gtan du 'khor ba
NK032(khi)005:919: ru 'khyams nyen yod pas nga rang 'di ru lcebs
NK032(khi)005:921: nga'i lus 'di shi yang sems la slob dpon gyi
NK032(khi)005:922: byin gyis brlabs nas 'khor ba ru gtan la mi
NK032(khi)005:923: 'khyams pa dgos te yong bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:924: ka pa li nas spu gri ka ma la bton
NK032(khi)005:925: nas ske la rgyab dgos sems nas dengs kyis byas
NK032(khi)005:926: tsa na / slob dpon dga' rab rdo rjes gzigs te zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:929: khyod ci 'dod pa yin gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)005:930: nga chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:931: tshe da res gcig pus sangs rgya ba gcig 'dod pa yin zhes zhus pas /
NK032(khi)005:932: khyod kyis da dung ma go'am zhes gsungs pa la /
NK032(khi)005:933: bdag gis ni ma rig ma rtogs ma go'o zhes zhus pas /
NK032(khi)005:934: phyag g.yas spyi bo ru bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)005:935: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:939: 'i gnyis su med pa'i don dbyer mi phyed pa /
NK032(khi)005:940: dbyer mi phyed pa'i dus na dbyer phyed bya ba'am /
NK032(khi)005:941: mi phyed bya ba'i blo'i mtha' 'am /
NK032(khi)005:942: tshig gi mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi
NK032(khi)005:943: gnas pa'i chos nyid kyi rang sgra'i ngang du zhag
NK032(khi)005:944: bdun gyi bar du ting nge 'dzin thun gcig tu
NK032(khi)005:946: de las sad tsa na rjes kyi shes pa la
NK032(khi)005:947: sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung
NK032(khi)005:948: gi ye shes chen po mun khung du sgron me
NK032(khi)005:949: bteg pa bzhin du byas pa bcos pa med par
NK032(khi)005:950: rang gsal du rgyud la lhag gis shar nas 'dug
NK032(khi)005:951: go // rgyud la shar ba'i don de yang mi
NK032(khi)005:952: brjed mi yal bar brten par bya ba'i brjed rdo
NK032(khi)005:953: go // ru / dga' rab rdo rjes /
NK032(khi)005:954: sur+y+aa d+ha ra zhes brdas bstan pas /
NK032(khi)005:955: khyed rang nyi ma'i snying po ya gi la ltos dang bya ba'i brda ru go nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:956: nyi ma'i snying po de dus gsum du 'du 'bral med pa /
NK032(khi)005:960: chos bzhi dang ldan pa gcig tu 'dug go //
NK032(khi)005:961: dpe de bzhin du rang gi sems nyid kyang chos bzhi dang ldan pa /
NK032(khi)005:962: gsal la rtog pa med pa nyi ma'i snying po lta bu gcig tu rtogs so //
NK032(khi)005:963: de yang bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs /
NK032(khi)005:964: rtogs pa tsam gyis don mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)005:965: sgrib pa la sbyangs dka' ba nyon mongs pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:966: shes bya'i sgrib pa de nyid du dag /
NK032(khi)005:967: thob pa la dka' ba mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob /
NK032(khi)005:968: thun mong gi dngos grub zhar la byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:969: dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na phub sog zhor la 'byung ba de bzhin no //
NK032(khi)005:970: de yang slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje'i phyag na
NK032(khi)005:971: mda' lnga bsnams pa de ye shes lnga ru go
NK032(khi)005:972: // gzhu dang sprad du 'dug pa de yang thabs
NK032(khi)005:973: dang shes rab ya ma bral bar zung du 'jug
NK032(khi)005:974: // par go // sham thabs thod du bcings pa
NK032(khi)005:975: de theg pa 'og ma ma spang bar gong ma
NK032(khi)005:976: dbyings su dag par go zhing rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:977: de'i dus su bka' skyong gi mkha' 'gro ma gsum gyis byin gyis brlabs /
NK032(khi)005:978: bka' skyong gi srung mar khas blangs dam bcas so //
NK032(khi)005:979: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen de yang bya 'phur ba'am rdzi bskyod pa bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:980: dur khrod gser gling nas dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du /
NK032(khi)005:981: zla ba ril po bcu gsum gyi lam yod pa la /
NK032(khi)005:982: gro khar phril gyis brtol lo //
NK032(khi)005:983: de ni slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi lo rgyus so //
NK032(khi)005:984: de nas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis rang bzhin gyis byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:985: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs la shar ba ni /
NK032(khi)005:986: dper na nyi zla la nye ring med kyang snod
NK032(khi)005:987: dag pa dang chu gtsang ma'i nang du 'char ba
NK032(khi)005:988: bzhin du / 'gro ba la nye ring med kyang
NK032(khi)005:989: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs la yang dag pa'i
NK032(khi)005:990: don la mos pa gcig rang bzhin gyis shar te
NK032(khi)005:991: bzhin du / / de yang nam tho rengs gcig tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:992: ga re bskal pa nas bskal par tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)005:993: bskal pa nas bskal par sgrib pa sbyangs kyang /
NK032(khi)005:994: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal las thar ram zer ba las /
NK032(khi)005:995: de'i gong du thar pa'i thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:996: yang dag par rdzogs pa'i sangs rgyas ni thams cad mkhyen pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:997: de'i chos byed pa ni rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs /
NK032(khi)005:998: grong khyer ser skya'i sgo kha dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang na /
NK032(khi)005:999: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya /
NK032(khi)005:1000: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya rgyal po'i mchod gnas su bzhugs yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:1001: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i chos yod dam med /
NK032(khi)005:1004: mi 'dug na yang de rang du kho thag chod bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1005: sh+r+ai sing has dpal na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du byon nas /
NK032(khi)005:1006: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya la spyan g.yas pas gzigs /
NK032(khi)005:1007: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta lnga brgya la spyan g.yon pas gzigs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1009: bskal pa nas bskal pa ru tshogs bsags /
NK032(khi)005:1010: bskal pa nas bskal pa ru sgrib pa sbyangs kyang /
NK032(khi)005:1011: bskal pa nas bskal pa gcig gam gnyis na 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal grol lam zer ba las /
NK032(khi)005:1012: de'i gong du grol thabs mi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1013: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i chos 'dra med dam /
NK032(khi)005:1014: de lta bu gcig med na ni /
NK032(khi)005:1015: de ring sang la dus btab pa'i mi yang stabs ka snga phyi en tsam zhig gis 'dzol nas /
NK032(khi)005:1016: gtan du mi 'phrad par yang 'gro ba yong gi 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1017: bskal pa grangs med pa gcig gam gnyis na glo
NK032(khi)005:1018: bur gyi nyon mongs pa'i rkyen gyis ci tsug 'gro
NK032(khi)005:1019: rang ci cha zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:1020: rgyu mtshan nyid kyi pan+di ta la rgyus med pas ci yang mi gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:1021: 'bras bu gsang sngags kyi pan+di ta rnams gcig nas gcig tu spyan zur gyi brdas bskul nas /
NK032(khi)005:1022: 'og ma dag des bzhengs nas lan btab pa /
NK032(khi)005:1023: 'o skol gyi 'di na de lta bu ni med de /
NK032(khi)005:1024: 'di nas nub phyogs su phyin pa na /
NK032(khi)005:1025: dur khrod chen po gser gling he chen brdal bya ba na /
NK032(khi)005:1026: sgrub pa'i gnas gser gyi brag phug yu ba can bya ba yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:1027: der rigs byed lha'i sprul pa slob dpon dga' rab rdo rje bya ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1028: bcom ldan 'das rdo rje sems dpa'i sprul pa sems dag lha'i bu zhes bya ba /
NK032(khi)005:1029: snang ba'i gzugs su grub la /
NK032(khi)005:1030: reg pa'i gzugs su ma grub pa /
NK032(khi)005:1031: nam mkha'i 'ja' lta bu gcig gis byin gyis brlabs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1032: skad cig ma'i don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs
NK032(khi)005:1033: rgya ba'i dgongs pa de khong la yod pa yin
NK032(khi)005:1034: pas / de gong du yang 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba 'dri ru byung ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1035: pan+di ta gong ma rnams kyis khong dga' rab rdo rje'i gam du lung bstan pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:1036: dga' rab rdo rje de mkha' 'gro ma rnams kyis
NK032(khi)005:1037: nub phyogs o rgyan yul sprin nag po 'dus pa'i
NK032(khi)005:1039: da lta 'jig rten mi yul na mi bzhugs /
NK032(khi)005:1040: khong gis byin gyis brlabs pa'i slob dpon 'jam dpal
NK032(khi)005:1041: bshes gnyen bya ba des skad cig ma'i don rtogs
NK032(khi)005:1042: nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i gdams pa 'di
NK032(khi)005:1043: lon nas / lho phyogs gyad kyi yul b+he ta la'i gling /
NK032(khi)005:1044: shing dra ba gtsug dgu yod pa'i tshal /
NK032(khi)005:1046: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du /
NK032(khi)005:1049: bya rmyang gcig gis brtol ba bzhin du zla ba bcu gsum gyi lam yod pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1050: dur khrod gser gling gi tsha ba thon nas byon
NK032(khi)005:1051: pas dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer du gro
NK032(khi)005:1052: khar hril gyis brtol nas byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1053: da lta khong de na bzhugs nas yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:1054: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba'i chos de khong la zhus na yong /
NK032(khi)005:1055: gzhan da lta yang chos de lta bu shes pa med zer ro //
NK032(khi)005:1056: de yang lho phyogs ni rgya gar rdo rje gdan gyi lho phyogs /
NK032(khi)005:1057: gyad kyi yul ni gyad stobs po che 'byung ba'i yul /
NK032(khi)005:1058: b+he ta la'i gling ni lho phyogs b+he ta la'i gling bya ba de yin /
NK032(khi)005:1059: shing dra ba gtsug dgu bkod pa'i tshal ni /
NK032(khi)005:1060: shing rigs mi gcig pa dgu'i nags dang tshal gyis rim par bskor ba yin /
NK032(khi)005:1061: gnod sbyin 'brog gnas kyi sa ni /
NK032(khi)005:1062: de ru 'gro ba'i lam ri bar gyi 'brog chen po yod pa'i sa na /
NK032(khi)005:1063: bsdo ba la sogs pas gnod sbyin mi ma yin gnas so //
NK032(khi)005:1064: mi phyugs byung tshad thams cad las kyis za bar bsdos pa yod pa'i sa yin /
NK032(khi)005:1065: de tsho brgal ba na dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer bya ba /
NK032(khi)005:1066: rigs pa'i gnas lnga la sogs pa'i yon tan ci
NK032(khi)005:1067: yang 'byung ba'i grong khyer chen po gcig yod pa'o
NK032(khi)005:1068: // sh+r+ai sing has grong khyer de ru 'gro ba
NK032(khi)005:1069: la nye ring dang dka' sla ci tsam yod dris
NK032(khi)005:1070: // pas / de ru 'gro ba la nye ring
NK032(khi)005:1071: ni mi yi yul med pa'i lung stong na phar
NK032(khi)005:1072: la 'gro ba la zla ba ril po bcu gsum
NK032(khi)005:1073: // pas / gyi lam yod / dka' sla ni
NK032(khi)005:1074: lam na gcan gzan sbrul gdug pa can rnams dang
NK032(khi)005:1075: // pas / gyi lam yod / / mi ma yin dang lha ma yin la sogs pa yod /
NK032(khi)005:1076: de yang gcan gzan gdug pa can dang 'phrad na khrum gyis zos nas 'gro /
NK032(khi)005:1077: sbrul gdug pa can dang 'phrad na lce leb kyis byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1078: snag ma tsho kha ru sib la rus pa rnams thang la spung gis yong ba yin /
NK032(khi)005:1079: lha ma yin dang 'phrad na skad bton pa tsam gyis mig khrag phrul gyis 'chi ba yin ste /
NK032(khi)005:1080: de lta bu med na nged kyang 'gro ste gsung ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1081: de ru sh+r+ai sing ha the tshom en cig zos te /
NK032(khi)005:1082: de bas nye ba'am 'jigs pa chung ba'i lam 'dra ba med dam byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1083: de las nye zhing 'jigs pa chung ba'i lam ni
NK032(khi)005:1084: ri'i khong seng sa'i phug pa gcig na phar phyin
NK032(khi)005:1085: na / zla ba ril po drug na sleb yong ba'i lam gcig yod de /
NK032(khi)005:1086: de'i lam nas phar la yang sbrul gdug pa can dang /
NK032(khi)005:1087: ri rab kyi khong seng na mi ma yin gyi grong khyer yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:1088: sbrul gdug pa can gyis nye mi nus pa la
NK032(khi)005:1089: rtsi ma gi ta zhes bya ba gla rtsi lus
NK032(khi)005:1090: la 'dogs dgos / mi ma yin gyi grong khyer
NK032(khi)005:1091: du 'khyams na ri rab kyi khong seng du 'khyams
NK032(khi)005:1092: nas phyi ru mi thon pas /
NK032(khi)005:1093: mi ma yin gyi grong khyer gyi sgo sgrib pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1094: zhun chen gyi mar me khyer nas phyin na /
NK032(khi)005:1095: zla ba ril po drug nas sleb yong ba'i lam gcig yod de byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1097: sh+r+ai sing has de ru 'tsho ba'i yo byad dang /
NK032(khi)005:1098: dgos pa'i rdzas rtsi ma gi ta lus la byug /
NK032(khi)005:1099: zhun chen gyi mar me khyer nas phyin pas zla
NK032(khi)005:1100: ba ril po drug na dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i
NK032(khi)005:1102: de ru slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba de bzhugs sam /
NK032(khi)005:1104: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba de /
NK032(khi)005:1105: nged kyi yul du byon nas /
NK032(khi)005:1106: lo phyugs rtag tu legs pa /
NK032(khi)005:1107: char chu dus su phebs pa /
NK032(khi)005:1108: mi nad dang phyugs nad rgyun chad pa la sogs
NK032(khi)005:1109: pa'i bkra shis pa dang yon tan shin tu 'phel
NK032(khi)005:1110: bar byung ba yin zer te /
NK032(khi)005:1111: kho rang nged kyis zhal mjal ba dang ngo shes pa med zer ro //
NK032(khi)005:1115: de skad zer ba las ngas shes zer ba ma byung nas /
NK032(khi)005:1116: de nas btsal bas kyang ma rnyed /
NK032(khi)005:1117: sdod pa yang ma tshugs te /
NK032(khi)005:1118: cam me cam mer phyin pas chu kha gcig tu sleb tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1119: bud med chu len pa gcig dang mjal nas gtam
NK032(khi)005:1120: gcig 'dri dgos bsam nas de ru 'dug dang byas
NK032(khi)005:1121: pas / lan med par bum pa rgyab tu khyug
NK032(khi)005:1122: gis khur nas mi sdod par 'gro bar 'dug pas
NK032(khi)005:1123: pas / / de ma 'thad par tshor nas sh+r+ai
NK032(khi)005:1124: sing has kyang gong du rdzu 'phrul gyi dngos grub
NK032(khi)005:1126: phyag g.yas pa kha sbub nas dengs kyis byas nas sa ni b+he sa byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1127: mo'i bum pa rgyab nas khog gi gog nas sa la khrig gis 'byar ro //
NK032(khi)005:1128: de ru mos kyang rdzu 'phrul can du ngo shes nas /
NK032(khi)005:1129: kha phyi ru log gi byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1130: so gseb nas shel dkar gyi gri chung cig car gyis bton nas /
NK032(khi)005:1131: tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa pra sa la zer nas brang kha shags kyi phyes te /
NK032(khi)005:1132: snying gi nang nas yang dag grub pa'i lha mo brgyad dpal dang dgu 'dug pa zhal bstan no //
NK032(khi)005:1133: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has kyang bud med rdzu 'phrul can gcig tu 'dug par shes nas /
NK032(khi)005:1134: sa ni sa ma ya dzahbyasa nas phyag g.yas pa yar la dengs byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1135: bum pa de sa nas khog gi gog nas mo rang gi rgyab tu khyug gis song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1137: tsit+ta a b+hi shiny+tsa mam zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1138: brang kha cag gis zum mo //
NK032(khi)005:1140: a b+hi shiny+tsa ni dbang bskur ba /
NK032(khi)005:1141: mam ni zhal gsum pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:1142: de ru sh+r+ai sing ha la yang dag thugs kyi ma brgyad dpal dang dgu'i zhal bstan /
NK032(khi)005:1143: dbang bskur nas zhal zum pa'o //
NK032(khi)005:1144: de nas mo na re khyod ci 'dod pa yin zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1145: nga ni gzhan ci yang mi 'dod de /
NK032(khi)005:1146: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen bya ba /
NK032(khi)005:1147: dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer bya ba 'di na bzhugs zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1148: 'tshol du yong ba la lam ma rnyed /
NK032(khi)005:1149: khyod kyi de 'dra ngo shes sam byas nas dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:1152: gzhan sus kyang ngo mi shes te /
NK032(khi)005:1153: nga rang dam rang gis bcas pa'i sring mo bka'
NK032(khi)005:1154: skyong gi mkha' 'gro ma sde gsum bya ba las
NK032(khi)005:1155: / nga'i ming 'bar ma'i gdong can bya ba yin te /
NK032(khi)005:1156: ltos dang zer nas ljags nar gyi brkyang bas /
NK032(khi)005:1157: spyi bo ru lhag gis sleb nas gdong pa la
NK032(khi)005:1158: me 'bar ba bzhin du dmar ring gis byung ngo
NK032(khi)005:1160: da khyed rang nga'i phyi ru 'dong ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1161: ngas slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen de bstan gyis zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1162: grong khyer der chu'i bum pa gnas su skyel ba'i tshul du byas nas phyir byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1163: ma gi yin no gsungs nas bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1164: btsun pa hral po gcig gis rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug /
NK032(khi)005:1165: gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la gzar nas /
NK032(khi)005:1166: sham thabs thod du bcings pa gcig gis glang la
NK032(khi)005:1167: lcag gis brab kyin zhing rmod du 'gro ba gcig
NK032(khi)005:1168: byung nas / de'i drung du phyin nas dang po nas chos zhu ma byas par /
NK032(khi)005:1169: btsun pa 'o skol la bza' ba gcig zhu dang byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1170: btsun pa de na re bza' ba 'di ru ga na 'ong /
NK032(khi)005:1171: grong ya gi na nga'i jo mo yod cing de ru slong dang zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1172: ga re 'di chos yod pa'i gzhung mi 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)005:1174: khrom btsun gcig yin tshod du 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)005:1175: gal te yin yang srid pas da dung du rdzi rtog dgos bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1176: jo mo de'i drung du phyi nas jo mo bza' bca' gcig zhu dang byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1177: khyod rang 'di ru sdod cig nga la spag med pas btsal nas yong gi zer nas song bas /
NK032(khi)005:1178: tshong 'dus su 'gro ba la nyin lam bdun yod
NK032(khi)005:1179: pa gcig jo mos yud cig la 'khor nas byi'u
NK032(khi)005:1180: mchil sprad bdun nyos nas thu bar blug nas gson
NK032(khi)005:1181: po ru khyer nas byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1182: mdun du slebs pa dang byi'u bdun po ltag pa phud nas bsad de /
NK032(khi)005:1183: spu btog rgyu long phyungs nas btsos te 'bras chan dang gnyis mkhar gzhong gi steng du drangs te /
NK032(khi)005:1184: spag med 'di gsol bar zhu zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1186: spyir nga btsun pa'i cha byad du yod pas sha'i rnam pa mi zhu /
NK032(khi)005:1187: de'i nang nas kyang dge slong gi cha byad yod pas mi zhu /
NK032(khi)005:1188: khyad par du yang nga la bsngosa nas bsad pa'i sha 'di lta bu mi zhu bas /
NK032(khi)005:1189: phar la bzhes par zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1190: rjes su yi rang chos par 'dug zer nas byi'u mchil sprad bdun po lag tu blang nas /
NK032(khi)005:1191: se gol gtogs pa gcig byas pas sbrul chil byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1192: nam mkha' la tsi di ri ri 'phur nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1193: de ru a ma jo mo 'dis kyang bsad gso
NK032(khi)005:1194: la sogs pa nus pa'i rdzu 'phrul can gcig 'dug
NK032(khi)005:1195: pas / de tsug tu song nas da ci'i btsun
NK032(khi)005:1196: pa de slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen rang min
NK032(khi)005:1197: pas / rgyu mi 'dug / da dung rdzi rtog bya dgos par 'dug bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1198: jo mo do nub gnas g.yar po zhu dgos byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1199: khyod rang de ru 'dug pas chog gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1200: de ru bsdad tsa na de ring gi btsun pa
NK032(khi)005:1201: hral po de de ru byung ste rtsa nas yar
NK032(khi)005:1203: nangs par snga ba nas sh+r+ai sing has rdo rje
NK032(khi)005:1204: sems dpa'i mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba zhal bton du
NK032(khi)005:1205: byas pas / khong gis ce re gsan nas /
NK032(khi)005:1207: don la lta ci smos te /
NK032(khi)005:1208: tshig la rmongs pa gsungs te /
NK032(khi)005:1210: don ma go ba ru 'dug pa bya ba ru byung bas /
NK032(khi)005:1211: der slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen yin 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1212: de min gzhan de 'dra ba mi yong bsam skad /
NK032(khi)005:1213: de nas btsun pa de na re /
NK032(khi)005:1214: jo mo spag tshol la shog /
NK032(khi)005:1215: da nang btsun pa 'di la tsha ba 'dren dgos gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1216: yang jo mo des tshong 'dus nas bud med kyi
NK032(khi)005:1217: lag pa g.yon pa gru mo man chad la gdub
NK032(khi)005:1218: bu lnga dang bcas pa gcig nyos nas byung bas
NK032(khi)005:1219: / de 'bras chan dang gnyis mkhar gzhong gi steng du drangs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1220: spag med 'di gsol bar zhu zer skad /
NK032(khi)005:1221: sngar bzhin du dge slong gi cha byad du yod pas sha'i rnam pa mi zhu /
NK032(khi)005:1222: de'i nang nas kyang mi'i sha mi zhu /
NK032(khi)005:1223: de'i nang nas kyang bud med kyi sha mi zhu bas /
NK032(khi)005:1224: phar la bzhes par zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1225: rjes su yi rang chos pa rang du 'dug zer
NK032(khi)005:1226: nas bud med kyi lag pa de nam mkha' la
NK032(khi)005:1228: se gol gtogs pa gcig mdzad pas /
NK032(khi)005:1229: 'od kha dog lnga dang bcas pa 'ja' lta bu
NK032(khi)005:1230: gcig tu byas nas nam mkha' la yal song skad
NK032(khi)005:1231: / de ru the tshom ma zos te /
NK032(khi)005:1232: btsun pa 'di slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen rang yin 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1233: jo mo 'di la yang rdzu 'phrul 'di lta bu 'dug pa bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1235: lha phyag dang bskor ba lan mang du byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1237: khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed du gsol byas
NK032(khi)005:1238: nas gsol ba btab cing zhu ba phul bas ci
NK032(khi)005:1240: de nas lha phyag nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du btsal /
NK032(khi)005:1241: bskor ba nyin lan gsum mtshan lan gsum du byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1242: zla ba ngo re la zhu ba'i don re phul kyang ci yang mi gsung nas /
NK032(khi)005:1243: da ni nam yang chos mi ster bar 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1244: nga rang gi yul du log nas 'gro dgos bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1245: khur tsa dang ka pa li dang khres po tsho btegs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1246: gdams ngag ma gnang kyang phyi phyag ga cig bya dgos bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1247: mchod khang du phyin pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:1248: sh+r+ai sing ha gsungs dbu btegs byung nas /
NK032(khi)005:1249: a byas pa dang ci yang mi gsung bar dbu hril gyis bstum nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1250: gzhan gdams ngag ni mi ster /
NK032(khi)005:1252: mchod khang gi sbur ma dang 'bag 'bog mi gtsang
NK032(khi)005:1253: ba 'di tsho phyogs bya bar byung bsam nas phyag
NK032(khi)005:1254: g.yas pas phrul du ser bu'am /
NK032(khi)005:1255: tshad rlangs gcig gis phyag kyang shul du btab nas byung ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1256: de ru lan bco brgyad du phyags dgos byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1257: thang chad nas slob dpon gyi mdun du krong nger ngal gsos nas yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1258: slob dpon gyi sngas na shing thog rdog po che ba kha dog legs pa /
NK032(khi)005:1260: da ci nga la 'bod pa de 'di rang zo byas pa yin nam bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1262: ro mchog brgya dang ldan pa gcig byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1263: de zos zin pa dang dug dang gyur te 'gyel
NK032(khi)005:1264: nas shi 'phras byed cing dug skyug gin du 'chi
NK032(khi)005:1266: sh+r+ai sing ha'i thugs la shi na rung bdun shar te /
NK032(khi)005:1267: ga re slob dpon gyis gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la bkal /
NK032(khi)005:1268: rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug nas byung ba'i
NK032(khi)005:1269: dus su chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin te 'dug
NK032(khi)005:1270: pa la / ngas ma go ba shi na rung bsam pa dang gcig /
NK032(khi)005:1271: byi'u mchil sprad bdun gyi sha drangs pa'i dus na chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1272: ngas ma go ba shi na rung bsam pa dang gnyis /
NK032(khi)005:1273: mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bton pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)005:1274: chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1275: ngas ma go ba shi na rung bsam pa dang gsum /
NK032(khi)005:1276: bud med kyi lag pa g.yon pa drangs pa'i dus
NK032(khi)005:1277: na yang chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa
NK032(khi)005:1278: la / ngas ma go bsam pa dang bzhi /
NK032(khi)005:1279: slob dpon la gser gyi man+dala phul /
NK032(khi)005:1280: phyag dang bskor ba byas nas gdams ngag zhus pa'i
NK032(khi)005:1281: dus na ci yang mi gsungs pa de chos nyid
NK032(khi)005:1282: kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1283: ngas ma go bsam pa dang lnga /
NK032(khi)005:1284: da nga rang 'gro dgos bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1285: mchod khang du phyin pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:1287: 'di phyogs bya ba yin nam bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1288: sbar sbur lan bco brgyad du phyags dgos byung ba
NK032(khi)005:1289: de chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la
NK032(khi)005:1290: / ngas ma go bsam pa dang drug /
NK032(khi)005:1291: de nas slob dpon gyi sngas na shing thog rdog po che ba kha dog legs pa /
NK032(khi)005:1293: 'di zo bya ba yin 'dug sems nas zos pas
NK032(khi)005:1294: dug tu gyur te skyug cing 'gyel nas 'chi ba
NK032(khi)005:1296: chos nyid kyi brda' gcig yin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1298: go ba med pa khyed rang shi na rung bsam pa dang bdun shar tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1300: skyug pa'i 'phro yang chad nas slob dpon gyi mdun du krong nger bsdad nas yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1304: nga ni chos nyid kyi don skad cig ma cig
NK032(khi)005:1305: gis don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis 'tshang rgya ba
NK032(khi)005:1306: zhig 'dod pa yin te byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1307: 'o na khyod kyis da dung ma go'am gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:1308: bdag gis ni ma rig ma go ma rtogs so zhus pas /
NK032(khi)005:1309: slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyis phyag g.yas pa
NK032(khi)005:1310: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i spyi bo ru brkyang nas
NK032(khi)005:1311: / a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1315: 'i ni gnyis su med pa'i don la dbye ru mi phyed de /
NK032(khi)005:1316: blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas
NK032(khi)005:1317: pa'i ngang du phril gyis zhag bdun gyi bar du
NK032(khi)005:1318: song ngo // ting nge 'dzin de las sad tsa
NK032(khi)005:1319: na rjes kyi shes pa la sems nyid dngos po
NK032(khi)005:1320: gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung gi ye shes chen
NK032(khi)005:1321: song ngo // po de / mun khung du sgron me btegs ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:1322: rang gsal du lhag ger rgyud la shar ro //
NK032(khi)005:1323: de'i don de brjed kyis dogs pa'am /
NK032(khi)005:1324: brtan par bya ba'i phyir mi brjed mi yal bar bya ba'i brjed rdo ru brdas bstan pa /
NK032(khi)005:1325: a wan d+ha ra zhes brdas bstan no //
NK032(khi)005:1326: de yang sh+r+ai sing ha la /
NK032(khi)005:1327: khyed rang nam mkha'i dkyil ya gi la ltos /
NK032(khi)005:1328: khyod rang gi rgyud la skyes pa de /
NK032(khi)005:1329: dper na nam mkha'i dkyil ya gi dang 'dra ba yin gyi bya ba'i brda' ru byung nas /
NK032(khi)005:1330: nam mkha'i dkyil du bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1331: nam mkha'i dkyil yar gnam sngon po la ma bltas /
NK032(khi)005:1332: mar sa rdo rab rib la ma bltas /
NK032(khi)005:1333: tshur kha lus dang sems la ma 'khris /
NK032(khi)005:1334: bar snang las gzhan la ma 'phros par /
NK032(khi)005:1335: mdun gyi nam mkha' 'dom gang gi tshad tsam du bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1336: mdun gyi nam mkha' 'di dang po rgyu las ma byung /
NK032(khi)005:1337: bar du rdzas su ma grub /
NK032(khi)005:1338: tha ma rkyen gang gis kyang mi 'jig ste /
NK032(khi)005:1339: gsal la ngos bzung med par 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1340: dpe de bzhin du rang gi sems nyid blo'i mtha'
NK032(khi)005:1341: zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa de
NK032(khi)005:1342: / dang po rgyu 'di las byung bya ba mi 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1343: bar du dngos rdzas su ma grub /
NK032(khi)005:1344: tha ma rkyen gang gis kyang mi 'jig pa /
NK032(khi)005:1345: 'dus ma byas pa blo'i mtha' zab cing phra ba tsam yang mi gnas pa /
NK032(khi)005:1346: gsal la rtog pa med pa /
NK032(khi)005:1347: nam mkha'i dkyil lta bu gcig rtogs so //
NK032(khi)005:1348: de ru slob dpon 'jam dpal bshes gnyen gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1349: ngas gnya' thong zung gcig phrag la gzar /
NK032(khi)005:1350: rmos thong zung gcig mdun du btsug pa'i dus su
