NK032(khi)005:1351: thabs shes rab gnyis kyi sgo nas bstan pa yin
NK032(khi)005:1353: byi'u mchil pa bdun gyi sha drangs pa de tshogs
NK032(khi)005:1354: drug ngo bo gcig tu bstan pa yin te khyod
NK032(khi)005:1355: kyis ma go / mdo sgyu 'phrul d+r+wa ba bton pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)005:1356: chos thams cad bsam brjod dang bral bar bstan pa yin te khyod kyis ma go /
NK032(khi)005:1357: bud med kyi lag pa g.yon pa gdub bu lnga
NK032(khi)005:1358: dang bcas pa gcig drangs pa'i dus su bud med
NK032(khi)005:1359: shes rab kyi rang bzhin la ye shes lngar 'char
NK032(khi)005:1360: bar bstan pa yin te khyod kyis ma go /
NK032(khi)005:1361: gser gyi man+dala phul nas phyag dang bskor ba byas
NK032(khi)005:1362: nas khyed kyi rtogs pa bdag la bskyed par zhu
NK032(khi)005:1364: ngas ci yang ma smras pa de don smra brjod
NK032(khi)005:1365: dang bral bar bstan pa yin te khyod kyis ma
NK032(khi)005:1366: go / sbar sbur lan bco brgyad du phyag tu
NK032(khi)005:1367: bcug pa de khyod la khams bco brgyad kyi sgrib
NK032(khi)005:1368: pa zab cing phra ba gcig 'dug pa de sbyong
NK032(khi)005:1369: ba'i phyir du bla ma'i mchod khang phyag bdar byed
NK032(khi)005:1370: du bcug pa yin te khyod kyis ma go /
NK032(khi)005:1371: shing thog kha dog legs pa rdog po che zhing
NK032(khi)005:1372: dri zhim pa de khyod phyi gzung ba'i yul la
NK032(khi)005:1373: chags pa yin / ro mchog brgya dang ldan par tshor ba de /
NK032(khi)005:1374: nang 'dzin pa'i sems la chags pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:1375: gzung 'dzin gnyis po dug tu gyur nas /
NK032(khi)005:1376: na nas shi la khad pa'i dus su /
NK032(khi)005:1377: shi na rung bdun byung bas bshags par song nas sgrib pa dag pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:1378: ngas kyang de gong nas bstan pa yin te /
NK032(khi)005:1379: khyod rang las sgrib che bas ma go ba yin skad /
NK032(khi)005:1380: de ru sgrib pa dag pas bstan pa tsam gyis rtogs /
NK032(khi)005:1381: rtogs pa tsam gyis mngon du gyur te /
NK032(khi)005:1383: sog phub zhor la 'byung ba bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:1384: mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob /
NK032(khi)005:1385: thun mong gi dngos grub zhar la byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1386: de nas bya 'phur ba'am rdzi bskyod pa'am gom pa
NK032(khi)005:1387: gcig gis 'gong pa'am bya rmyang gcig gis slebs pa
NK032(khi)005:1389: sh+r+ai sing ha dpal yon tan 'byung ba'i grong khyer nas tsha ba thon nas byon pas /
NK032(khi)005:1390: rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs grong khyer ser skya'i
NK032(khi)005:1391: sgo khang na yod pa'i dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug
NK032(khi)005:1392: lag khang du gro kha ru slebs so //
NK032(khi)005:1393: rdo rje gdan gyi byang phyogs na tshur la phyi pa mu stegs pa'i rtsod pa dar bas /
NK032(khi)005:1394: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa nub la khad pa /
NK032(khi)005:1395: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing has tshar bcad nas /
NK032(khi)005:1396: nang pa sangs rgyas pa'i bstan pa dar zhing rgyas par mdzad de /
NK032(khi)005:1397: dgra bcom pa lnga brgya'i dpon mdzad do //
NK032(khi)005:1398: de nas rgya gar nas tshe 'phos nas bod du
NK032(khi)005:1399: sku 'khrungs pa'i mnga' bdag byang chub sems dpa' khri
NK032(khi)005:1400: srong lde'u btsan gyi snyan du gsan /
NK032(khi)005:1401: thugs kyis kyang mkhyen nas bsam yas su /
NK032(khi)005:1403: li khra mi la sogs rgya mi bdun bya ba bsags nas /
NK032(khi)005:1404: 'o skol gyi bod na rgyu 'bras kyi chos bshad de dar na yang /
NK032(khi)005:1407: yul rgya gar gyi yul na /
NK032(khi)005:1408: rgyu 'bras kyi chos mtha' dag las bogs phyung ba /
NK032(khi)005:1409: bka' sems phyogs kyi chos man ngag gi don skad
NK032(khi)005:1410: cig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas pa'i
NK032(khi)005:1412: 'o skol de lta bu zhu ru btang dgos gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1413: rgya mi mi bdun la sogs pa rnams gros byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1415: de lta bu zhu ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1416: su to mu to ci yin cha med pa btang bas phan mi thogs te /
NK032(khi)005:1417: lam na 'phrang dgu dang gcan dgu la sogs pa dka' ba'i 'phrang mang po yod pas /
NK032(khi)005:1419: nor yar shor nas ngan pa phyis 'gyod na mi yong bas /
NK032(khi)005:1423: 'dis lon yong zer ba'i kha 'cham pa /
NK032(khi)005:1424: phyis mi 'gyod pa gcig btang dgos zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1425: de ru bod kyi mo ma la mkhas pa dpe ni gu bya ba li'i yul la sa bkug /
NK032(khi)005:1426: rgya nag po'i dpyad mkhan la mkhas pa b+he shog pra bya ba rgya nag po'i yul nas bkug /
NK032(khi)005:1427: pra mkhan la mkhas pa pra se na bya ba
NK032(khi)005:1428: rgya dkar po'i yul nas bkug ste de ru mo
NK032(khi)005:1431: mkhas pa'i mthar thug pa de gsum kha 'cham ste /
NK032(khi)005:1432: de lta bu'i chos gzhan sus kyang mi lon te /
NK032(khi)005:1433: yul gtsang gi snye mo bye mkhar bya ba na /
NK032(khi)005:1435: yum bran bza' sgron skyid bya ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1436: pa gor gan 'jag thang ta bya ba byis pa
NK032(khi)005:1437: lo brgyad lon pa gcig yod pa de btang na
NK032(khi)005:1438: lon / gzhan sus kyang mi lon zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1439: de ru mnga' bdag rgyal pos /
NK032(khi)005:1440: blon 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga tsam khrid nas /
NK032(khi)005:1441: gtsang gi snye mo bye mkhar du byon te /
NK032(khi)005:1442: gnas gcig 'dug pa'i sgo mdun du bsgug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1443: rgyal po gzi brjid che ba dang /
NK032(khi)005:1444: phyag dang zhe sa mi shes pas /
NK032(khi)005:1445: nyi ma phyi phrang tshun chad du mjal 'phrad ma nus te /
NK032(khi)005:1447: de nas sgo mdun du byis pa ra lu can gcig byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1448: mnga' bdag rgyal pos byis pa de la zhal kyal ku re'i thabs su dri ba byas te /
NK032(khi)005:1449: byis pa khyod kyi pha ga ru song byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1450: nga'i pha gtam 'tshol du song zer /
NK032(khi)005:1451: ma ga ru song byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1454: nga 'gro ba'i don la 'gro ba yin zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1455: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1456: kha brda' dang la nye bzang /
NK032(khi)005:1457: nged rang 'dod pa'i bu de rang yin nam gsungs skad /
NK032(khi)005:1458: byis pa de pa gor he 'dod kyi bu pa gor gan 'jag yin te /
NK032(khi)005:1459: dpal rnam par snang mdzad kyi sprul pa bee ro tsa na bya ba yin /
NK032(khi)005:1460: mnga' bdag rgyal po de yang rigs gsum mgon po'i sprul pa yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:1461: kha brda dang la nye yang 'di ltar du go ste /
NK032(khi)005:1462: pha gtam 'tshol du song ba de rgya gar gyi chos kyi gtam 'tshol du 'gro bya bar go /
NK032(khi)005:1463: ma mig 'tshol du song bya ba de ma rig
NK032(khi)005:1464: mun pa sel ba'i man ngag mig lta bu 'tshol
NK032(khi)005:1466: nga rang 'gro ba'i don la phyin pa yin zer ba de /
NK032(khi)005:1467: ngas kyang 'gro ba'i don byas na 'ong ba yin bya ru go ba lags skad /
NK032(khi)005:1468: der pa gor he 'dod kyis zhugs kyang sgron /
NK032(khi)005:1471: zhabs don ci mnga' zhes dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:1473: rgya gar gyi yul na chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1474: tshe gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i chos yod zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1475: de zhu ru gtong ba la gzhan sus kyang mi yong bas /
NK032(khi)005:1476: khyod kyi bu 'dis yong zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1477: khyod kyi bu 'di slong du 'ong ba yin gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1478: nga'i bu lo brgyad las ma lon pas /
NK032(khi)005:1479: rgya gar du cang sleb bam /
NK032(khi)005:1480: chos zhu ba yang yong ngam zer te /
NK032(khi)005:1482: nged da lta gtong ba min gyis /
NK032(khi)005:1483: dus lan gcig gtong ba yin zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1484: der gan 'jag brtan bza' mi mar la khrid nas /
NK032(khi)005:1486: bee ro tsa na brag dmar bsam yas su khrid nas /
NK032(khi)005:1487: lo brgyad kyi bar du nyin grib mtshams su bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)005:1488: zas su dkar gsum gsol zhing /
NK032(khi)005:1489: shes rab bskyed pa'i gzungs dang /
NK032(khi)005:1491: der lo bcu drug lon pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:1493: gser gyi pa tra bdun brdungs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1494: thod pa'i dbyibs su bu ga mang po phug nas mgo la bkab ste /
NK032(khi)005:1496: na len tra'i bu gtsang sngon po legs grub bya
NK032(khi)005:1497: ba lo nyi shu rtsa lnga lon pa gcig dang
NK032(khi)005:1498: gnyis kyis / bsam yas kyi ar+ya pa lo'i gling du /
NK032(khi)005:1499: rmi lam brtags pas bzang nas gshegs so //
NK032(khi)005:1500: de nas 'phrang dgu gcan dgu ru la lar glu blangs /
NK032(khi)005:1503: dka' ba'i spyod pa sna tshogs mdzad nas gshegs so //
NK032(khi)005:1504: de nas sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang du /
NK032(khi)005:1505: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha la chos zhus pas /
NK032(khi)005:1506: lo gcig tu bka' sems phyogs gsungs te /
NK032(khi)005:1507: rgya gar du slob bu byas /
NK032(khi)005:1509: bod bu gnyis po go'am tshim mam gsungs te /
NK032(khi)005:1510: gtsang sngon po legs grub zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1514: sngon la bod du gshegs te 'phrang bas bkrongs so //
NK032(khi)005:1515: bee ro tsa na'i thugs la /
NK032(khi)005:1516: dang po thos pa'i shes rab sgra 'ba' zhig tu 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1517: bar du bsam pa'i shes rab sgra don phyed mar 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1518: tha ma sgom pa'i shes rab don du 'dug kyang /
NK032(khi)005:1519: de yang thos bsam sgom gsum gyis rgyud sbyangs dgos par 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1520: skad gcig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas pa'i chos de mi 'dug bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1522: gser gyi pa tra bdun mgo nas phud nas /
NK032(khi)005:1523: phyis nas slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha'i phyag tu phul te /
NK032(khi)005:1524: slob dpon sh+r+ai sing ha lags /
NK032(khi)005:1525: mnga' bdag khri srong lde'u btsan gyi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1526: chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas tshe
NK032(khi)005:1527: gcig gis sangs rgya ba'i chos slob dpon la yod
NK032(khi)005:1528: mchis pas / bdag zhu ru btang ba lags pas /
NK032(khi)005:1529: chab gser 'di dag kyang rje'i phyag nas bskur ba lags pas /
NK032(khi)005:1530: slob dpon gyi phyag tu bsnams la /
NK032(khi)005:1531: skad cig mas don rtogs nas tshe gcig gis sangs
NK032(khi)005:1532: rgya ba'i gdams ngag de thugs la gdags par zhu
NK032(khi)005:1533: lags / de thugs la ma btags na /
NK032(khi)005:1534: bdag bod du phyin kyang rgyal pos bka' chad bcad nas /
NK032(khi)005:1535: chab la gsol te mchi bas /
NK032(khi)005:1536: thugs la gdags par zhu 'tshal ces zhus pas /
NK032(khi)005:1537: slob dpon gyi phyag g.yon pa na gser gyi pa tra bsnams /
NK032(khi)005:1538: g.yas pa bee ro tsa na'i spyi bor brkyangs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1539: a ha ho'i zhes byin gyis brlabs /
NK032(khi)005:1541: chos nyid kyi rang sgra zhag bdun gyi bar du yal bar byung ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1542: der sems nyid dngos po gshis kyi gnas lugs rang byung gi ye shes chen po de /
NK032(khi)005:1543: mun khung du sgron me btegs pa bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:1544: thugs su lhag gis gsal lo //
NK032(khi)005:1545: de las sad tsa na bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1546: slob dpon yang de rang na bzhugs nas 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)005:1547: de'i dus de'i tshe san d+ha ra zhes brdas su bstan no //
NK032(khi)005:1548: de khyod rang man shel 'di la ltos dang bya ba ru go nas /
NK032(khi)005:1549: bltas pas rin po che man shel de rkyen kha dog rnam pa lnga /
NK032(khi)005:1550: gang gis thog tu bzhag pa de bzhin du /
NK032(khi)005:1551: kho yang kha dog 'gyur byin 'dug ste /
NK032(khi)005:1552: gang la yang ma brten pa'i dus na /
NK032(khi)005:1553: gsal ba la ngo bo gang yang ma grub pa gcig tu 'dug pas /
NK032(khi)005:1555: don rang gi mtshan nyid chos bzhi dang ldan pa de /
NK032(khi)005:1556: ma rtogs pa'i dus na rkyen gyis cir yang 'char gin 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1557: rkyen gang la yang ma brten pa'i dus na /
NK032(khi)005:1558: gsal la ngo bo gang du yang ma grub pa gcig rtogs so //
NK032(khi)005:1559: der nyon mongs pa'i sgrib pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:1560: shes bya'i sgrib pa dag nas /
NK032(khi)005:1561: chos nyid kyi don la rtogs pa mngon du gyur nas /
NK032(khi)005:1562: mchog gi dngos grub de nyid du thob /
NK032(khi)005:1563: thun mong gi dngos grub zhar la byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1564: dper na 'bras 'khor ma lo legs na sog phub zhar la 'byung ba bzhin no //
NK032(khi)005:1565: de nas slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i thugs la /
NK032(khi)005:1566: da bod du 'gro dgos bsam pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1567: gtsang legs grub 'phrang bas bsad pas /
NK032(khi)005:1568: som nyi en cig zos pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1569: slob dpon sh+r+ai seng ha'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1570: chu 'di dag la brten pa'i gru //
NK032(khi)005:1571: skya ba drag pos rtsol phod na //
NK032(khi)005:1572: grus kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)005:1573: gzhu mo dag la brten pa'i mda' //
NK032(khi)005:1574: skyes bu'i mtheb kyis rtsol phod na //
NK032(khi)005:1575: mdas kyang pha rol phyin par 'gyur //
NK032(khi)005:1576: yon tan dag la brten pa'i mi //
NK032(khi)005:1577: sa phyogs bgrod kyang nyam mi nga //
NK032(khi)005:1579: bee ro tsa na the tshom med par gshegs te /
NK032(khi)005:1580: dpal sh+r+ai na len+d+ra'i gtsug lag khang nas tsha ba
NK032(khi)005:1581: thon nas phyin pas bsam yas su gro khar brtol
NK032(khi)005:1582: lo // de yan chad ni rig 'dzin brdas grol ba'i brgyud pa yin no ////
NK032(khi)005:1583: de nas rgya gar gyi chos skyong ba'i rgyal po d+harma r+aa dza'i rmi lam log ste /
NK032(khi)005:1584: bod du theg pa chen po'i chos thun mong ma yin pa gcig shor nas 'dug sems nas /
NK032(khi)005:1586: bod spre'u brag srin gyi bu yin pas /
NK032(khi)005:1587: bod du theg pa chen po'i chos shor du 'phangs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1588: rkang mgyogs pa song la bod du phra ma chug cig gsung ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1589: der zhag bdun na rkang mgyogs pa mi bdun gyis bsam yas su brtol te /
NK032(khi)005:1590: bod du gcig gis ngan sngags dang /
NK032(khi)005:1591: dug sbyor bslus nas song bas /
NK032(khi)005:1593: de spyug cig sod cig zer nas song ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1594: de nas li rtag po che'am /
NK032(khi)005:1595: li khra mi la sogs pa /
NK032(khi)005:1597: mnga' bdag las col chung ba med /
NK032(khi)005:1598: chos nyid kyi don skad cig mas rtogs nas tshe gcig gi sangs rgyas pa yod zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1599: de zhu ru btang ba yin na /
NK032(khi)005:1600: gnod bya mang po slob tu bcug nas ci byed /
NK032(khi)005:1601: mnga' bdag la dgra ni mi yong na /
NK032(khi)005:1602: da bod phung 'gro bas 'di spyugs pa las mi
NK032(khi)005:1603: btub zer nas mnga' bdag gis slob dpon spyugs par
NK032(khi)005:1604: byas te / mi btsun pa dbang chung ba ngan la rid pa gcig bzung nas /
NK032(khi)005:1608: slob dpon spyugs pa yin no gsungs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1609: zangs gtsang po las bskyur ro //
NK032(khi)005:1610: de nas slob dpon gyi thugs kyis bzung bas /
NK032(khi)005:1611: zangs de 'ol kha mkhar ltag yang snang gi 'khor mar chags so //
NK032(khi)005:1612: der 'khor ma'i bdag pos zangs de rnyed nas /
NK032(khi)005:1613: kha phye bas mi gcig byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1614: 'di glud du btang ba'i mi gcig 'dug zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1615: gsos pas 'ol kha rgyug thang gi lhu mi yin skad /
NK032(khi)005:1616: de nas slob dpon dbu rtse'i glo 'bur du bzhugs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1617: rgyal po la chos gsungs bzhin yod pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1618: jo mo tshe spong bza' zhe sdang che bas /
NK032(khi)005:1620: rgyal po gar 'gro ba bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1621: rgyal po slob dpon la drung mar yang drangs /
NK032(khi)005:1622: dar gyi thod phud nas khrus bshal byed cing yod pa de mos mthong nas /
NK032(khi)005:1623: der mo rang bdas pas ma zin te /
NK032(khi)005:1624: mos rnga bo che brdungs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1627: mnga' bdag las col chung ba med de /
NK032(khi)005:1628: slob dpon de da rung 'dug go //
NK032(khi)005:1629: chu la bskyur ba de sprang po yin 'dug go zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1631: mnga' bdag las col chung ba med /
NK032(khi)005:1632: gser dngul la sogs pa'i rin po che thams cad gyang gi logs la byug /
NK032(khi)005:1633: chos len du gtong zer nas ngan sngags dang dug sbyor dang khro chu mtheb rgya can bslus /
NK032(khi)005:1634: slob dpon spyugs par byas nas sprang po chu la 'bor /
NK032(khi)005:1635: da yang spyugs dgos zer nas rgyal po blon 'khor nyi shu rtsa lnga dang bcas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1636: skyi gtsang la brgal nas 'gro ba'i dus der /
NK032(khi)005:1637: slob dpon ma dgyes nas mgur bzhengs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1638: jo mo 'gyod nas da mi gshegs par zhu byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1640: sems kyi thag pa de gong du bcad /
NK032(khi)005:1641: gru'i nyag thag de tshur la thong zer nas gshegs so //
NK032(khi)005:1642: der tsha ba rong gi la khar bskyal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1643: da rung yar la gshegs par zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1646: blon 'khor tsho yar la log go //
NK032(khi)005:1647: der slob dpon tsha ba rong gi ri la bzhugs yod pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1648: bod kyi bya slob dpon gyi phyi la 'brangs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1650: rgyal mo dpal gzher 'phan bu la sogs pa na re /
NK032(khi)005:1651: bod kyi bya nged kyi yul du byung bas /
NK032(khi)005:1652: bod kyis nged kyi yul 'phrog pa'i so rtogs pa yin pas de ring ri nyul dgos zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1653: btsal bas slob dpon rnyed nas /
NK032(khi)005:1654: drud bshal brdung btsogs mang po byas /
NK032(khi)005:1655: sbal dong dang shig dong du bcug ste /
NK032(khi)005:1656: slob dpon chos nyid kyi ngang la bzhugs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1657: sbal pa dang shig gis za ma nus te /
NK032(khi)005:1659: bod stong sbos gcig 'dug zer nas mchod gnas byas so //
NK032(khi)005:1660: der tsha ba rong pa la chos ston dgos bsam nas /
NK032(khi)005:1661: sgra shes sam mi shes bltas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1662: mi mang po 'tshogs pa'i sa ru /
NK032(khi)005:1663: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK032(khi)005:1666: mdos se mdos se gne 'bol gne khri ldos se ldos se rne sbom khri yang snang /
NK032(khi)005:1668: bya ba las ma byung ste /
NK032(khi)005:1669: byis pa ngan la rid pa gcig na re /
NK032(khi)005:1670: rdo rje sems dpa' sems dpa' che //
NK032(khi)005:1673: ma ni snga gong nas shi /
NK032(khi)005:1674: pha yod kyang dwa phrug tu 'dug na zer ro //
NK032(khi)005:1675: 'di nga'i g.yog bya yis chos slob nga la slong byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1676: 'o de bod kyi stong sbos la sbyin /
NK032(khi)005:1677: nged rang tsho lto ster res bya'o zer nas byin no //
NK032(khi)005:1678: kho la sgra dang chos slob pas /
NK032(khi)005:1679: rgyal mo g.yu sgra snying po de lags /
NK032(khi)005:1680: de nas r+ts+wa mi shing mi'i tshong pas bod bskor nas byung ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1682: mnga' bdag rgyal po'i mchod gnas su ji ltar bya ba bzhugs 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1683: mnga' bdag sku khams bde bar 'dug gam /
NK032(khi)005:1684: rgyal khrims ma zhig par 'dug gam /
NK032(khi)005:1688: mnga' bdag sku khams bde bar 'dug /
NK032(khi)005:1689: mchod gnas bi ma la mi tra bzhugs 'dug zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1690: bee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1692: khong ya gi na theg pa chen po'i chos gsungs nges med pas /
NK032(khi)005:1693: khyod nga yi la yog dor la shog gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:1695: zhwa spyi ring gcig gi nang du /
NK032(khi)005:1696: snga 'gyur lnga shog dril du byas nas bcug ste gyon nas bsam yas su byon no //
NK032(khi)005:1697: slob dpon bi ma la mi tras /
NK032(khi)005:1698: theg pa chung ngu'i gyi chos gsung gi 'dug pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1699: g.yu sgra snying pos zhwa gyon 'ber ka gcig btsugs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1701: ka ka pa ri ka ka pa ri zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1703: brda thim brda thim zhes skad 'phang smas nas gsungs so //
NK032(khi)005:1704: der gnyags ku m+aa ra yi zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1705: sprang po a tsa ra ku co re che /
NK032(khi)005:1707: khyed gnyis kyi sgra de ngas ma shes zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1710: pho rog rdo rje 'gros kyis sa mi chod //
NK032(khi)005:1711: nyan thos byis pa'i chos kyis 'tshang mi rgya //
NK032(khi)005:1712: theg pa chen po'i chos mi bshad par zer ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1713: ngas brda thim byas pa de /
NK032(khi)005:1714: dus la ma bab kha rog sdod byas pa yin /
NK032(khi)005:1715: kho chos shes pa gcig 'dug zer nas btsal bas /
NK032(khi)005:1716: gling bar nas ma jo chang ma gcig gi gam du 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)005:1717: khyod kyi chos ci shes dris pas /
NK032(khi)005:1718: bee ro tsa na bya ba'i slob ma yin /
NK032(khi)005:1719: bka' rdzogs pa chen po shes /
NK032(khi)005:1720: mdo khams smad nas 'ongs pa yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:1721: a tsa ra dz+ny+aa nas 'o na chos gcig zhu byas pas /
NK032(khi)005:1722: yang na rig pa dang rig pa barje /
NK032(khi)005:1723: yang na rig pa yon gyis bslu /
NK032(khi)005:1724: yang na rig pa bu la byin bya ba yin zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1725: der rig pa dang rig pa yang barjesa te /
NK032(khi)005:1726: a tsa ra dz+ny+aa nas bi ma la mi tra'i lo ts+aa ba byas nas /
NK032(khi)005:1727: phyi 'gyur bcu gsum g.yu sgra snying po la phar bshad /
NK032(khi)005:1728: g.yu sgra snying pos snga 'gyur rnam pa lnga /
NK032(khi)005:1729: a tsa ra dz+ny+aa na la bshad do //
NK032(khi)005:1730: rig pa yon gyis kyang bslus te /
NK032(khi)005:1731: slob dpon du khur nas sring mo zhabs tog tu phul ba lags so //
NK032(khi)005:1732: skabs der g.yu sgra snying po bod du song nas /
NK032(khi)005:1733: slob dpon bee ro tsa na skyo bar gyur nas /
NK032(khi)005:1734: rgyal mo tsha ba'i shod bya ba na bzhugs pa de /
NK032(khi)005:1735: rgyal mo tsha ba'i shod bya ba nas mar la
NK032(khi)005:1736: nyin lam bcu gsum gyi thag ring ba'i sa na
NK032(khi)005:1737: / rgyal mo stag rtse la khar bya ba na /
NK032(khi)005:1738: spang mi pham mgon po bya ba /
NK032(khi)005:1739: dgung lo dgu bcu rtsa lnga lon pa /
NK032(khi)005:1741: dad pa che ba gcig dang mjal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1743: slob dpon bee ro tsa na bya ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1744: skad cig mas don rtogs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1745: tshe gcig gis sangs rgyas ba'i chos yod zer ba la /
NK032(khi)005:1746: khyed der chos nyan gyin mi sdod par /
NK032(khi)005:1747: 'di na mar yong ba stangs re zhan zer bas /
NK032(khi)005:1748: de lta bu shes pa'i bee ro tsa na bya ba de nga rang yin gsungs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1749: der dga' nas shi na rung snyam tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1750: ma shi ba nga re 'tsheng zer nas /
NK032(khi)005:1752: nyin zhag phrug gcig tu ma btang ngo //
NK032(khi)005:1753: de nas bsgres pa ru 'dug nas /
NK032(khi)005:1754: phyag spyi bo ru bzhag nas /
NK032(khi)005:1755: a ha ho'i zhes brdas byin gyis brlabs pas /
NK032(khi)005:1756: so so skye bo ru 'dug pa dang /
NK032(khi)005:1757: las sgrib che bas go ru ma btub nas /
NK032(khi)005:1758: skyabs 'gro khyad par can la brten nas /
NK032(khi)005:1760: don sgrar btub tshad tshig tu bshad /
NK032(khi)005:1761: smra ru ma btub pa brdas su bstan /
NK032(khi)005:1762: de ru brda' sems kyi yul du bstan /
NK032(khi)005:1763: ngag rna ba'i dbang por blugs nas /
NK032(khi)005:1765: don rang gi chings su bstan /
NK032(khi)005:1766: der sems nyid de so so'i gnas lugs /
NK032(khi)005:1767: ma nor ba de la sgom du med kyang /
NK032(khi)005:1768: mi 'gyur mi yengs par byed pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1769: lus tshugs ma thub pa las /
NK032(khi)005:1770: pus 'khyud kyis bcings kyang 'gyel bas sgom rten btsug /
NK032(khi)005:1771: don nyams su myong ba de la yid ches par byed pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1772: tshul shing la blta yin bsgom du bcug go //
NK032(khi)005:1773: lus ngag yid gsum smin par dang grol bar byed pa la /
NK032(khi)005:1774: yang dag gi dbang bzhi rdzogs su bskur ba yin /
NK032(khi)005:1775: de sgom tshul bla ma'i byin rlabs zer ba yin gsungs /
NK032(khi)005:1776: de nas yang mi pham mgon pos brda la ngang gis blta yin yod tsa na /
NK032(khi)005:1777: slob dpon bee ro tsa na'i zhal nas /
NK032(khi)005:1778: mi pham mgon po'i drung du phyag rgya mtho do mdzad nas /
NK032(khi)005:1780: bdag nyid bee ro tsa na mchis pa 'di //
NK032(khi)005:1781: yang dag bcu gcig don dang ye nas ldan //
NK032(khi)005:1782: rgya gar yul nas chos slob nas //
NK032(khi)005:1783: sgra don bsdebs nas bka' bsgyur te //
NK032(khi)005:1784: mnga' bdag rgyal po nyid la gtad //
